(41, '2006-10-17 12:10:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2011-08-22 11:59:29', 'andrew', 'Hello, we''re Shark! Design &amp; Marketing.', '', 'Shark! is a Yorkshire based <strong>DESIGN AND MARKETING</strong> agency based between Huddersfield and Halifax. We''re experts in "graphic design":portfolio/design-for-print, "branding":portfolio/branding, strategy, "digital":portfolio/digital and print.\r\n\r\nOur ideas are always creative, original and results driven.\r\n\r\nWe work with brands of all shapes and sizes. Whether you are an established business looking for a fresh approach or launching a new product in to a crowded market, we have the experience and expertise to produce campaigns that generate real results.\r\n\r\nSome agencies might call themselves full service, integrated communications, media neutral, above the line, below the line or through the line. We prefer to call ourselves hard working and committed to our clients.\r\n\r\nWe think our work will speak for itself. Have a look through our portfolio, case studies and latest news. \r\nIf you like what you see, "get in touch...":contact', '	<p>Shark! is a Yorkshire based <strong><span class="caps">DESIGN</span> <span class="caps">AND</span> <span class="caps">MARKETING</span></strong> agency based between Huddersfield and Halifax. We&#8217;re experts in <a href="http://www.sharkdesign.co.uk/portfolio/design-for-print">graphic design</a>, <a href="http://www.sharkdesign.co.uk/portfolio/branding">branding</a>, strategy, <a href="http://www.sharkdesign.co.uk/portfolio/digital">digital</a> and print.</p>\n\n	<p>Our ideas are always creative, original and results driven.</p>\n\n	<p>We work with brands of all shapes and sizes. Whether you are an established business looking for a fresh approach or launching a new product in to a crowded market, we have the experience and expertise to produce campaigns that generate real results.</p>\n\n	<p>Some agencies might call themselves full service, integrated communications, media neutral, above the line, below the line or through the line. We prefer to call ourselves hard working and committed to our clients.</p>\n\n	<p>We think our work will speak for itself. Have a look through our portfolio, case studies and latest news. <br />\nIf you like what you see, <a href="http://www.sharkdesign.co.uk/contact">get in touch&#8230;</a></p>', '', '', '280,281,282,283,284,285,286,287,288,289,290,291,292,293,294,295,296,297,298,299,300,302,302,303,304,305,306,307,308,309,310,311,312,313,314', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 0, 'home', '', '', 'home', '00', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '3bfdf1588bdfd74b299189446de70ef4', '2006-10-17'),
(61, '2008-10-28 18:47:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2013-08-09 10:31:50', 'andrew', 'Design For Print', '', 'Tactile and emotive, we love designing for print. From brochures, stationery and logo''s, to point of sale, exhibition graphics and even leather bound pattern books it''s all about creating an experience that engages the end user and delivers your message in a trustworthy and authoritative manner. \r\n\r\nWe''ve bags of experience using the huge array of creative printing techniques available from foil blocking and glitter varnishes to die cutting, embossing and fragrance sampling. What''s more, we''re continually exploring the latest materials available to help give your product or service even greater impact.\r\n\r\nUsing the latest CAD software we''re also able to create unique and exclusive point of sale units or eye-catching retail displays to grab shopper attention.\r\n\r\n"Click here to see some examples of our most recent work":portfolio/design-for-print', '	<p>Tactile and emotive, we love designing for print. From brochures, stationery and logo&#8217;s, to point of sale, exhibition graphics and even leather bound pattern books it&#8217;s all about creating an experience that engages the end user and delivers your message in a trustworthy and authoritative manner. </p>\n\n	<p>We&#8217;ve bags of experience using the huge array of creative printing techniques available from foil blocking and glitter varnishes to die cutting, embossing and fragrance sampling. What&#8217;s more, we&#8217;re continually exploring the latest materials available to help give your product or service even greater impact.</p>\n\n	<p>Using the latest <span class="caps">CAD</span> software we&#8217;re also able to create unique and exclusive point of sale units or eye-catching retail displays to grab shopper attention.</p>\n\n	<p><a href="http://www.sharkdesign.co.uk/portfolio/design-for-print">Click here to see some examples of our most recent work</a></p>', '', '', '', 'Design-For-Print', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'what-we-do', '', '', 'design-for-print-services', '03', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '550f4d1d79b9af77d042f59c5e02e339', '2008-10-28'),
(54, '2013-10-22 13:51:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2013-10-22 13:51:51', 'andrew', 'Key Staff', '', 'All the team at Shark! must have a good sense of humour as well as being committed to delivering great work to all our clients. We aim to make every project fun and rewarding for everyone involved by being approachable, honest and sometimes even saying no!', '	<p>All the team at Shark! must have a good sense of humour as well as being committed to delivering great work to all our clients. We aim to make every project fun and rewarding for everyone involved by being approachable, honest and sometimes even saying no!</p>', '', '', '42,43,212,307', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'about', '', '', 'key-staff', '02', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'f04ebccb3740e29c706bc0e1c8931ea3', '2008-01-12'),
(43, '2008-10-16 19:39:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2012-11-27 12:22:37', 'andrew', 'Branding', '', 'Branding is much more than just a logo; it''s the very essence of a business. It should be a true reflection of your company''s values, from how you answer the phone to its online presence. Starting with a brand audit and then identifying your brand essence we have 13 years experience in creating strong, relevant and coherent brand communication strategies.\r\n\r\n"Click here to see some examples of how we''ve helped our clients create their brand":portfolio/branding', '	<p>Branding is much more than just a logo; it&#8217;s the very essence of a business. It should be a true reflection of your company&#8217;s values, from how you answer the phone to its online presence. Starting with a brand audit and then identifying your brand essence we have 13 years experience in creating strong, relevant and coherent brand communication strategies.</p>\n\n	<p><a href="http://www.sharkdesign.co.uk/portfolio/branding">Click here to see some examples of how we&#8217;ve helped our clients create their brand</a></p>', '', '', '', 'Branding', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'what-we-do', '', '', 'branding-services', '01', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '05d4be3c023b9cc20295156c4134d9f1', '2006-10-17'),
(60, '2008-10-28 09:19:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2009-03-11 10:14:48', 'kevin', 'Direct Marketing', '', 'Direct Marketing isn''t just about the stuff that comes through your letterbox, in fact, it rarely is. Direct marketing is about generating quantifiable results that can be used to guide future strategies and tactics. We employ the basic principles of Targeting, Timing and Proposition. It is important to know your real return on investment (ROI).\r\n\r\nDirect marketing is an essential part of almost everything we do at Shark!', '	<p>Direct Marketing isn&#8217;t just about the stuff that comes through your letterbox, in fact, it rarely is. Direct marketing is about generating quantifiable results that can be used to guide future strategies and tactics. We employ the basic principles of Targeting, Timing and Proposition. It is important to know your real return on investment (<span class="caps">ROI</span>).</p>\n\n	<p>Direct marketing is an essential part of almost everything we do at Shark!</p>', '', '', '', 'Direct-Marketing', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'what-we-do', '', '', 'direct-marketing-services', '02', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0deedf634cf596a44dc50d8a193b3a39', '2008-10-28'),
(55, '2008-02-08 19:50:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2010-02-18 11:48:01', 'andrew', 'What We Do', '', 'We adopt a ''style and substance'' approach to every project, no matter what the discipline or media. \r\n\r\nAll our creative, strategic and digital work is produced in-house and we have a great relationship with our network of production specialists.\r\n\r\nClick the links on the right to see some of things we do...', '	<p>We adopt a &#8216;style and substance&#8217; approach to every project, no matter what the discipline or media. </p>\n\n	<p>All our creative, strategic and digital work is produced in-house and we have a great relationship with our network of production specialists.</p>\n\n	<p>Click the links on the right to see some of things we do&#8230;</p>', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'what-we-do', '', '', 'what-we-do', '00', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '259a41015806ddc14c02db92c29dce61', '2008-02-09'),
(62, '2008-10-28 19:42:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2009-11-19 17:22:49', 'Andrew', 'Select Group Yorkshire Ltd', '', 'When the Select Group of companies grew ten-fold they needed a brand strategy that embraced their growing number of divisions. We developed a flexible identity system that defined each division, maintained the group identity and has the capacity to grow with the Select Group of companies. Alongside the brand strategy we produced all of Select''s corporate clothing - from hard wearing fleeces to hard hats, vehicle livery, stationery and brochures. We also created a hard working website which we maintain and optimise on a monthly basis. *Launch the site here - <a href="http://www.selectconstruction.co.uk/" title="Select" target="_blank" >Select</a>*\r\n\r\nWhat the client said:\r\n\r\n"We needed to work with someone who could understand our business and advise us on the best way forward. We appointed Shark! and they''ve been brilliant from start to finish, they have really allowed us to focus on what we''re good at, building."', '	<p>When the Select Group of companies grew ten-fold they needed a brand strategy that embraced their growing number of divisions. We developed a flexible identity system that defined each division, maintained the group identity and has the capacity to grow with the Select Group of companies. Alongside the brand strategy we produced all of Select&#8217;s corporate clothing &#8211; from hard wearing fleeces to hard hats, vehicle livery, stationery and brochures. We also created a hard working website which we maintain and optimise on a monthly basis. <strong>Launch the site here &#8211; <a href="http://www.selectconstruction.co.uk/" title="Select" target="_blank" >Select</a></strong></p>\n\n	<p>What the client said:</p>\n\n	<p>&#8220;We needed to work with someone who could understand our business and advise us on the best way forward. We appointed Shark! and they&#8217;ve been brilliant from start to finish, they have really allowed us to focus on what we&#8217;re good at, building.&#8221;</p>', 'When the Select Group of companies grew ten-fold they needed a brand strategy that embraced their growing number of divisions...', '	<p>When the Select Group of companies grew ten-fold they needed a brand strategy that embraced their growing number of divisions&#8230;</p>', '45,46,47,48,49', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'select-group', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '1c3da2a920f9702fd1978a3ee790b69a', '2008-10-28'),
(63, '2008-10-28 19:44:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2009-09-23 13:13:18', 'Andrew', 'Dugdale', '', 'Dugdale needed a new approach in order to market their latest range of suit fabric in the Far East. Alongside the team at Dugdale we developed a quintessentially English name, strategy and highly successful range of marketing material that has a real gentleman''s club feel. We produced stationery and literature with a foil blocked, hand drawn crest and also developed a patterned, leather outer for the bunch books - something which has never been seen before.\r\n\r\nAs well as working with Dugdale on the Thomas Fisher brand we have also helped to launch a sister brand called Joseph Hirst which maintains the traditional typographical flourish.\r\n\r\nWhat the client said:\r\n\r\n"Their attention to detail and their ability to translate ideas and concepts is natural and consistent, transforming our company and it''s image." - Robert Charnock, Director\r\n\r\n*Launch the site here - <a href="http://www.dugdalebros.com" title="Dugdale Website" target="_blank" >Dugdale website</a>*', '	<p>Dugdale needed a new approach in order to market their latest range of suit fabric in the Far East. Alongside the team at Dugdale we developed a quintessentially English name, strategy and highly successful range of marketing material that has a real gentleman&#8217;s club feel. We produced stationery and literature with a foil blocked, hand drawn crest and also developed a patterned, leather outer for the bunch books &#8211; something which has never been seen before.</p>\n\n	<p>As well as working with Dugdale on the Thomas Fisher brand we have also helped to launch a sister brand called Joseph Hirst which maintains the traditional typographical flourish.</p>\n\n	<p>What the client said:</p>\n\n	<p>&#8220;Their attention to detail and their ability to translate ideas and concepts is natural and consistent, transforming our company and it&#8217;s image.&#8221; &#8211; Robert Charnock, Director</p>\n\n	<p><strong>Launch the site here &#8211; <a href="http://www.dugdalebros.com" title="Dugdale Website" target="_blank" >Dugdale website</a></strong></p>', 'Alongside the team at Dugdale we developed a quintessentially English name, strategy and highly successful range of marketing material...', '	<p>Alongside the team at Dugdale we developed a quintessentially English name, strategy and highly successful range of marketing material&#8230;</p>', '51,52,53,54,55', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'dugdale', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'd77d83a5b67c9cbb3d0874ce25b4d6d4', '2008-10-28'),
(64, '2008-11-28 19:45:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2009-12-21 16:15:39', 'Andrew', 'Swimbabes', '', 'When we met Swimbabes it was obvious they had a really great product - their baby swim lessons. But their branding was confused and dated, and the online store wasn''t performing.\r\n\r\nWe helped them to create a slick and dynamic brand strategy that reflected the core values of the company and allowed them to expand the range of products they offer. \r\n\r\nThen we totally overhauled their existing e-commerce site making it easier to navigate, purchase from and be found on search engines. The re-designed website has been a great success and is a great site for parents on the go. \r\n\r\n*Launch the site here - <a href="http://www.swimbabes.co.uk" title="Swimbabes Website" target="_blank" >Swimbabes | The shop for little swimmers</a>*\r\n\r\nSince appointing Shark, Swimbabes have enjoyed lesson growth and have expanded to new pools in the area. Onlline sales are *up 205%* and Google Ad word costs are *down 54%!*. The online store repayed the cost of investment within 3 months, much to the delight of the client! \r\n\r\nIf you''re looking to increase your online sales and grow your business then give us a call on 01422 375 333. ', '	<p>When we met Swimbabes it was obvious they had a really great product &#8211; their baby swim lessons. But their branding was confused and dated, and the online store wasn&#8217;t performing.</p>\n\n	<p>We helped them to create a slick and dynamic brand strategy that reflected the core values of the company and allowed them to expand the range of products they offer. </p>\n\n	<p>Then we totally overhauled their existing e-commerce site making it easier to navigate, purchase from and be found on search engines. The re-designed website has been a great success and is a great site for parents on the go. </p>\n\n	<p><strong>Launch the site here &#8211; <a href="http://www.swimbabes.co.uk" title="Swimbabes Website" target="_blank" >Swimbabes | The shop for little swimmers</a></strong></p>\n\n	<p>Since appointing Shark, Swimbabes have enjoyed lesson growth and have expanded to new pools in the area. Onlline sales are <strong>up 205%</strong> and Google Ad word costs are <strong>down 54%!</strong>. The online store repayed the cost of investment within 3 months, much to the delight of the client! </p>\n\n	<p>If you&#8217;re looking to increase your online sales and grow your business then give us a call on 01422 375 333. </p>', 'When we met Swimbabes it was obvious they had a really great product - their baby swim lessons. But their branding was confused and dated, and the online store wasn''t performing.', '	<p>When we met Swimbabes it was obvious they had a really great product &#8211; their baby swim lessons. But their branding was confused and dated, and the online store wasn&#8217;t performing.</p>', '56,57,58,59,60', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'swimbabes', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'ca62e80781faf94121faac988f9ed2c2', '2008-10-28'),
