(68, '2008-10-28 19:49:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2014-02-20 16:07:24', 'andrew', 'Branding', '', 'Shark! design & marketing have 15 years experience developing strong, enduring and coherent brand communications for our clients. Always fresh, flexible and founded on one original idea we make sure our brand strategies work across all media and are a true reflection of your brands'' essence and personality.\r\n\r\nHave a look at the slide show above for a glimpse of some of our work and if you think we can help you "get in touch...":contact', '	<p>Shark! design &amp; marketing have 15 years experience developing strong, enduring and coherent brand communications for our clients. Always fresh, flexible and founded on one original idea we make sure our brand strategies work across all media and are a true reflection of your brands&#8217; essence and personality.</p>\n\n	<p>Have a look at the slide show above for a glimpse of some of our work and if you think we can help you <a href="http://www.sharkdesign.co.uk/contact">get in touch&#8230;</a></p>', '', '', '401,369,370,156,149,68,69,70,61,62,63,64,66', 'Branding', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'portfolio', '', '', 'branding', '01', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '4f5f06cf9a595839f8cbd3e691338113', '2008-10-28'),
(45, '2008-07-07 21:13:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2008-11-02 15:57:59', 'kevin', 'Shark! design win Towngate pitch', '', 'Shark! have been selected by Towngate plc (one of the North of England''s leading commercial and industrial property specialists!) to develop their new website and boost Towngate''s online presence. After a rigourous pitch process we were awarded the project because of our digital expertise and innovative/strategic thinking.\r\n\r\nAfter working predominantly with Leeds based agencies Julia (Marketing manager of Towngate) was impressed and delighted to have such an approachable and innovative agency available locally.', '	<p>Shark! have been selected by Towngate plc (one of the North of England&#8217;s leading commercial and industrial property specialists!) to develop their new website and boost Towngate&#8217;s online presence. After a rigourous pitch process we were awarded the project because of our digital expertise and innovative/strategic thinking.</p>\n\n	<p>After working predominantly with Leeds based agencies Julia (Marketing manager of Towngate) was impressed and delighted to have such an approachable and innovative agency available locally.</p>', 'Yorkshire based Shark! have been selected by Towngate Plc...', '	<p>Yorkshire based Shark! have been selected by Towngate Plc&#8230;</p>', '104', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-design-win-towngate-pitch', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '9c28633949667c86dbde649f71bf1ffa', '2007-08-17'),
(69, '2008-10-28 19:50:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2013-10-18 17:03:13', 'andrew', 'Digital', '', 'In an ever changing digital world, you need to be confident that your agency has the knowledge to engage and influence the new digital audience. The Shark! team have an exceptional track record in web design, content managed and e-commerce websites, e-mail marketing, Search Engine Optimization (SEO) and keyword analysis. \r\n\r\nTake a look at some of our digital projects in the slide show above and click on the links below to visit some of the websites we have designed and built.\r\n\r\nIf you''re unsure which form of digital communication will achieve the best results for your business why not give us a call?\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.wlprint.co.uk" title="W&L Website" target="_blank" >Waddington & Ledger Ltd</a>\r\nCMS web site design and build and galleries.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.originprintsolutions.co.uk" title="Origin Print Solutions website" target="_blank" >Origin Print Solutions</a>\r\nDesign and build of website featuring client area for creating and ordering personalised statonery. \r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.trinityacademyhalifax.org" title="Trinity Academy website" target="_blank" >Trinity Academy</a>\r\nContent managed website design and build. Featuring Twitter feed and video. \r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.tog24.com" title="TOG24 website" target="_blank" >TOG24</a>\r\nDesign and build. Flash movies, interactive javascript features, csv data capture.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.goldcrestchemicals.co.uk/" title="Goldcrest Chemicals website" target="_blank" >Goldcrest Chemicals</a>\r\nCMS website design and build including flash movies and photography. \r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.swimbabes.co.uk" title="Swimbabes website" target="_blank" >Swimbabes</a>\r\nDesign and development of CMS e-commerce site. \r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.gatewaysschool.co.uk" title="Gateways website" target="_blank" >Gateways School</a>\r\nCMS website design and build, unique folding menu, student blog, event calendar, and photography.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.towngate.plc.uk" title="Towngate website" target="_blank" >Towngate Plc</a>\r\nDesign and development of CMS website. Quick search, promotional banner, image rotators, csv data capture. \r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.theyorkshiresaucery.com" title="The Yorkshire Saucery Website" target="_blank" >The Yorkshire Saucery</a>\r\nDesign, build and interactive javascript features. \r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.rastrick.calderdale.sch.uk/" title="Rastrick School" target="_blank" >Rastrick School</a>\r\nCMS website design and build, with concertina folding menu.', '	<p>In an ever changing digital world, you need to be confident that your agency has the knowledge to engage and influence the new digital audience. The Shark! team have an exceptional track record in web design, content managed and e-commerce websites, e-mail marketing, Search Engine Optimization (<span class="caps">SEO</span>) and keyword analysis. </p>\n\n	<p>Take a look at some of our digital projects in the slide show above and click on the links below to visit some of the websites we have designed and built.</p>\n\n	<p>If you&#8217;re unsure which form of digital communication will achieve the best results for your business why not give us a call?</p>\n\n	<p><a href="http://www.wlprint.co.uk" title="W&L Website" target="_blank" >Waddington &amp; Ledger Ltd</a><br />\n<span class="caps">CMS</span> web site design and build and galleries.</p>\n\n	<p><a href="http://www.originprintsolutions.co.uk" title="Origin Print Solutions website" target="_blank" >Origin Print Solutions</a><br />\nDesign and build of website featuring client area for creating and ordering personalised statonery. </p>\n\n	<p><a href="http://www.trinityacademyhalifax.org" title="Trinity Academy website" target="_blank" >Trinity Academy</a><br />\nContent managed website design and build. Featuring Twitter feed and video. </p>\n\n	<p><a href="http://www.tog24.com" title="TOG24 website" target="_blank" >TOG24</a><br />\nDesign and build. Flash movies, interactive javascript features, csv data capture.</p>\n\n	<p><a href="http://www.goldcrestchemicals.co.uk/" title="Goldcrest Chemicals website" target="_blank" >Goldcrest Chemicals</a><br />\n<span class="caps">CMS</span> website design and build including flash movies and photography. </p>\n\n	<p><a href="http://www.swimbabes.co.uk" title="Swimbabes website" target="_blank" >Swimbabes</a><br />\nDesign and development of <span class="caps">CMS</span> e-commerce site. </p>\n\n	<p><a href="http://www.gatewaysschool.co.uk" title="Gateways website" target="_blank" >Gateways School</a><br />\n<span class="caps">CMS</span> website design and build, unique folding menu, student blog, event calendar, and photography.</p>\n\n	<p><a href="http://www.towngate.plc.uk" title="Towngate website" target="_blank" >Towngate Plc</a><br />\nDesign and development of <span class="caps">CMS</span> website. Quick search, promotional banner, image rotators, csv data capture. </p>\n\n	<p><a href="http://www.theyorkshiresaucery.com" title="The Yorkshire Saucery Website" target="_blank" >The Yorkshire Saucery</a><br />\nDesign, build and interactive javascript features. </p>\n\n	<p><a href="http://www.rastrick.calderdale.sch.uk/" title="Rastrick School" target="_blank" >Rastrick School</a><br />\n<span class="caps">CMS</span> website design and build, with concertina folding menu.</p>', 'In an ever changing digital media environment, you need to be confident that your agency has the knowledge to engage and influence the new digital audience. The Shark! in-house web team have an exceptional track record in web design', '	<p>In an ever changing digital media environment, you need to be confident that your agency has the knowledge to engage and influence the new digital audience. The Shark! in-house web team have an exceptional track record in web design</p>', '372,251,172,166,168,167,161,165,16