(154, '2014-02-20 16:48:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2014-02-20 17:08:41', 'andrew', '3D Retail Planning', '', 'Planning a new product launch or in-store promotion and want to see how it would work before it happens?\r\n \r\nOne of our clients was faced with this challenge and asked for our help visualising new point of sale concepts in a retail environment.\r\n \r\nOur 3D plan enabled them to explore different concepts and ways of improving the overall shopper experience.\r\n \r\nIf you''re looking for similar visual insight, give us a call today on 01422 376446.\r\n \r\n \r\n', '	<p>Planning a new product launch or in-store promotion and want to see how it would work before it happens?</p>\n\n	<p>One of our clients was faced with this challenge and asked for our help visualising new point of sale concepts in a retail environment.</p>\n\n	<p>Our 3D plan enabled them to explore different concepts and ways of improving the overall shopper experience.</p>\n\n	<p>If you&#8217;re looking for similar visual insight, give us a call today on 01422 376446.</p>', 'Planning a new product launch or in-store promotion and want to see how it would work before it happens?\r\nOne of our clients was faced with this challenge and asked for our help visualising new point of sale concepts in a retail environment. Our 3D plan enabled them to explore different concepts and ways of improving the overall shopper experience.', '	<p>Planning a new product launch or in-store promotion and want to see how it would work before it happens?<br />\nOne of our clients was faced with this challenge and asked for our help visualising new point of sale concepts in a retail environment. Our 3D plan enabled them to explore different concepts and ways of improving the overall shopper experience.</p>', '396,400,398,397,399', 'pos-packaging', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', '3d-retail-planning', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '338aef4b1faaf002ac24001f90f9a552', '2014-02-20'),
(70, '2008-10-28 19:51:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2014-02-21 10:32:04', 'andrew', 'Design For Print', '', 'Shark! love designing for print. From brochures, stationery and logo''s, packaging to point of sale, display material and even leather bound pattern books we''ve helped all our clients present their brand, promote their business, communicate a key message and attract new customers through print. \r\n\r\nOur understanding of creative print techniques available from foil blocking and embossing, to die-cutting and debossing, varnishing and fragrance sampling enables us to create print that is memorable, engaging and has stand-out.\r\n\r\nWhen executed effectively, printed media plays a vital and complimentary role in any communications strategy so why not get in touch and let us show you how we can help.\r\n\r\nTake a look at some of our design for print in the slide show above.', '	<p>Shark! love designing for print. From brochures, stationery and logo&#8217;s, packaging to point of sale, display material and even leather bound pattern books we&#8217;ve helped all our clients present their brand, promote their business, communicate a key message and attract new customers through print. </p>\n\n	<p>Our understanding of creative print techniques available from foil blocking and embossing, to die-cutting and debossing, varnishing and fragrance sampling enables us to create print that is memorable, engaging and has stand-out.</p>\n\n	<p>When executed effectively, printed media plays a vital and complimentary role in any communications strategy so why not get in touch and let us show you how we can help.</p>\n\n	<p>Take a look at some of our design for print in the slide show above.</p>', '', '', '410,408,406,403,389,378,363,373,356,346,330,375,402,309,349,290,250,347,202,348,350,245,226,', 'Design-For-Print', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'portfolio', '', '', 'design-for-print', '03', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'fbd9566360b46ceffdffb4a4ad2986be', '2008-10-28'),
(46, '2007-08-18 18:37:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2010-02-18 12:26:36', 'andrew', 'Contact Us', '', 'If you want to have a chat about a particular project or want to see more of our work you can get in touch by calling 01422 376446, or emailing us at "info@sharkdesign.co.uk":mailto:info@sharkdesign.co.uk.\r\n\r\nAlternatively fill out the form below and we will contact you shortly.\r\n\r\nAll fields are required.\r\n\r\n <txp:zem_contact to="info@sharkdesign.co.uk"  label="" subject="Shark! Website Enquiry" form="form_contact" label="" thanks_form="form_contact_thanks"/>\r\n\r\nShark! Design & Marketing\r\nThe W&L Building,\r\nLowfields Way,\r\nElland,\r\nHX5 9DA\r\n\r\nRegistered in England No:\r\n581 7121', '	<p>If you want to have a chat about a particular project or want to see more of our work you can get in touch by calling 01422 376446, or emailing us at <a href="mailto:info@sharkdesign.co.uk">info@sharkdesign.co.uk</a>.</p>\n\n	<p>Alternatively fill out the form below and we will contact you shortly.</p>\n\n	<p>All fields are required.</p>\n\n <txp:zem_contact to="info@sharkdesign.co.uk"  label="" subject="Shark! Website Enquiry" form="form_contact" label="" thanks_form="form_contact_thanks"/>\n\n	<p>Shark! Design &amp; Marketing<br />\nThe W&amp;L Building,<br />\nLowfields Way,<br />\nElland,<br />\nHX5 9DA</p>\n\n	<p>Registered in England No:<br />\n581 7121</p>', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 0, 'contact', '', '', 'contact-us', '00', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'a7347497fe6de27afeabb3efdd889597', '2007-08-18'),
(65, '2008-10-28 19:47:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2013-08-09 11:46:09', 'andrew', 'Client List', '', 'Here''s a list of some of the people who have chosen to work with Shark Design & Marketing:\r\n\r\n\r\np{width:220px;float:left;}. Hobbycraft\r\nHalco Rock Tools\r\nTerberg DTS\r\nNew Ivory\r\nPPG Architectural Coatings UK\r\nSolarLex\r\nGran Deco \r\nWilkinsons\r\nBrilliant Interiors\r\n\r\np{width:220px;float:left;}. Kilsaran International\r\nLister Horsfall\r\nRRAM Energy\r\nMNB Partnership\r\nElland Developments\r\nGateways School\r\nRastrick High School\r\nQueen Elizabeth Grammar School\r\nTrinity Academy, Halifax', '	<p>Here&#8217;s a list of some of the people who have chosen to work with Shark Design &amp; Marketing:</p>\n\n	<p style="width:220px; float:left;">Hobbycraft<br />\nHalco Rock Tools<br />\nTerberg <span class="caps">DTS</span><br />\nNew Ivory<br />\n<span class="caps">PPG</span> Architectural Coatings UK<br />\nSolarLex<br />\nGran Deco <br />\nWilkinsons<br />\nBrilliant Interiors</p>\n\n	<p style="width:220px; float:left;">Kilsaran International<br />\nLister Horsfall<br />\n<span class="caps">RRAM</span> Energy<br />\n<span class="caps">MNB</span> Partnership<br />\nElland Developments<br />\nGateways School<br />\nRastrick High School<br />\nQueen Elizabeth Grammar School<br />\nTrinity Academy, Halifax</p>', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'get-info', '', '', 'client-list', '01', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '5848ee65baf29ef90b1dc5db6f88e5bf', '2008-10-28'),
(150, '2013-09-11 16:52:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2013-09-11 16:52:52', 'andrew', 'Hobbycraft - Back to School', '', 'National retailer Hobbycraft has a great selection of fun products for getting kids kitted out for ''Back to School.'' \r\nShark Design & Marketing were chosen to design eye-catching in-store point of sale including headers, shelf strips, posters and window kits to help drive sales across this range.\r\n\r\nUsing a combination of vibrant colours, sponge lettering (everyone remembers sponge letters!) and stationery items we gave their ''Back to School'' aisle real stand out. \r\n\r\nIf you looking to give your product ''stand out'' in a busy retail environment why not give us a call.....\r\n', '	<p>National retailer Hobbycraft has a great selection of fun products for getting kids kitted out for &#8216;Back to School.&#8217; <br />\nShark Design &amp; Marketing were chosen to design eye-catching in-store point of sale including headers, shelf strips, posters and window kits to help drive sales across this range.</p>\n\n	<p>Using a combination of vibrant colours, sponge lettering (everyone remembers sponge letters!) and stationery items we gave their &#8216;Back to School&#8217; aisle real stand out. </p>\n\n	<p>If you looking to give your product &#8216;stand out&#8217; in a busy retail environment why not give us a call&#8230;..</p>', 'National retailer Hobbycraft has a great selection of fun products for getting kids kitted out for ''Back to School.'' \r\nShark Design & Marketing were chosen to design eye-catching in-store point of sale including headers, shelf strips, posters and window kits to help drive sales across this range.\r\n', '	<p>National retailer Hobbycraft has a great selection of fun products for getting kids kitted out for &#8216;Back to School.&#8217; <br />\nShark Design &amp; Marketing were chosen to design eye-catching in-store point of sale including headers, shelf strips, posters and window kits to help drive sales across this range.</p>', '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'hobbycraft-back-to-school', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'c62727c5ed197f9cf3ae6f2dca062a15', '2013-09-11'),
(47, '2007-08-18 19:21:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2010-02-18 11:44:28', 'andrew', 'Who We Are', '', 'We are a straight talking, friendly team who are intensely passionate about what we do. We operate with creativity, integrity and honesty. \r\n\r\nHelping our clients fulfil their objectives and grow their business is our ultimate goal. We believe in simple clear messages, originality in delivery and making the whole process fun for everyone involved.\r\n\r\nOur Philosophy\r\n\r\n_Every client is the same..._\r\n\r\nNo matter how big or small, all our clients get the same treatment. Pro-active account handling, a strategic approach to every project and results driven executions.\r\n\r\n_Every client is different..._\r\n\r\nWe don''t use a ''9 step plan'' or a ''one size fits all'' creative process. We approach each project individually and deliver intelligent, tailor made answers to our clients brief.', '	<p>We are a straight talking, friendly team who are intensely passionate about what we do. We operate with creativity, integrity and honesty. </p>\n\n	<p>Helping our clients fulfil their objectives and grow their business is our ultimate goal. We believe in simple clear messages, originality in delivery and making the whole process fun for everyone involved.</p>\n\n	<p>Our Philosophy</p>\n\n	<p><em>Every client is the same&#8230;</em></p>\n\n	<p>No matter how big or small, all our clients get the same treatment. Pro-active account handling, a strategic approach to every project and results driven executions.</p>\n\n	<p><em>Every client is different&#8230;</em></p>\n\n	<p>We don&#8217;t use a &#8217;9 step plan&#8217; or a &#8216;one size fits all&#8217; creative process. We approach each project individually and deliver intelligent, tailor made answers to our clients brief.</p>', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 0, 'about', '', '', 'who-we-are', '01', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '80f0c9f3b0419768dc5f61f9a09bb486', '2007-08-18'),
(49, '2008-10-16 21:04:32', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2012-11-27 12:22:51', 'andrew', 'Digital', '', 'In an ever changing environment, you need to know that the agency you work with understands the medium. The Shark! in-house web team have an exceptional track record in digital media and our specialist knowledge includes: websites, E-Commerce, Search Engine Optimisation and E-mail.\r\n\r\n"Click here to see some examples of how we''ve helped our clients create their website.":portfolio/digital', '	<p>In an ever changing environment, you need to know that the agency you work with understands the medium. The Shark! in-house web team have an exceptional track record in digital media and our specialist knowledge includes: websites, E-Commerce, Search Engine Optimisation and E-mail.</p>\n\n	<p><a href="http://www.sharkdesign.co.uk/portfolio/digital">Click here to see some examples of how we&#8217;ve helped our clients create their website.</a></p>', '', '', '', 'Digital', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'what-we-do', '', '', 'digital-services', '02', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'fe00be249fcf77598861744da76c3263', '2007-08-18'),
(71, '2008-10-28 19:51:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2014-02-20 16:05:29', 'andrew', 'Logos &amp; Stationery', '', 'At Shark, original ideas and creative thinking is at the heart of everything we do -whether that is a distinctive logo, new visual identity or suite of stationery.\r\n\r\nTake a look at some examples of our work above...', '	<p>At Shark, original ideas and creative thinking is at the heart of everything we do -whether that is a distinctive logo, new visual identity or suite of stationery.</p>\n\n	<p>Take a look at some examples of our work above&#8230;</p>', '', '', '401,289,288,241,240,170,171,284,89,90,91,98,70,92,93,94,95,96,96,99,240,241', 'Logos-Stationery', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'portfolio', '', '', 'logos-stationery', '06', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '9e6a9290aeb67426794afe0a444137a6', '2008-10-28'),
(121, '2011-02-09 15:30:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2011-02-10 21:04:59', 'andrew', 'Queen Elizabeth Grammar School magazine', '', 'QEGS Junior School, Wakefield wanted a new look for their annual magazine. With the help of four of their budding designers, Shark created an understated but eye-catching design with engaging imagery to bring the highlights of the school year to life. This printed celebration is such a great read we couldn¹t put it down!', '	<p><span class="caps">QEGS</span> Junior School, Wakefield wanted a new look for their annual magazine. With the help of four of their budding designers, Shark created an understated but eye-catching design with engaging imagery to bring the highlights of the school year to life. This printed celebration is such a great read we couldn¹t put it down!</p>', 'QEGS Junior School, Wakefield wanted a new look for their annual magazine...', '	<p><span class="caps">QEGS</span> Junior School, Wakefield wanted a new look for their annual magazine&#8230;</p>', '211', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'queen-elizabeth-grammar-school-magazine', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '5845e0a37dcfa2b0ed69a5e0694b3e5b', '2011-02-09'),
(72, '2008-10-29 10:00:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2009-03-11 10:15:55', 'kevin', 'Newsletter Sign Up', '', 'Want to keep up to date on all things Shark!? Sign up for our quarterly newsletter to receive information on Shark!, case studies, research and interesting things we''ve come across. Don''t worry we aren''t going to pass your details on to any 3rd parties.\r\n\r\nAll fields are required.\r\n\r\n <txp:zem_contact to="info@sharkdesign.co.uk"  label="" subject="Shark! Newsletter Signup" form="form_contact_subscribe" label="" thanks_form="form_contact_subscribe_thanks"/>', '	<p>Want to keep up to date on all things Shark!? Sign up for our quarterly newsletter to receive information on Shark!, case studies, research and interesting things we&#8217;ve come across. Don&#8217;t worry we aren&#8217;t going to pass your details on to any 3rd parties.</p>\n\n	<p>All fields are required.</p>\n\n <txp:zem_contact to="info@sharkdesign.co.uk"  label="" subject="Shark! Newsletter Signup" form="form_contact_subscribe" label="" thanks_form="form_contact_subscribe_thanks"/>', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'contact', '', '', 'newsletter-sign-up', '01', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '00dcedb6bb8b17ff5227991c9a02266c', '2008-10-29'),
(73, '2008-11-02 14:44:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2011-03-07 17:46:17', 'andrew', 'TOG 24', '', 'TOG 24 appointed Shark! to design and develop their new brand website. The brief: to create a site that reflects the new brand essence (Discover Freedom) and promotes the exciting new winter range......in just 6 weeks.\r\n\r\nThe new site launched on time and on budget. Eye-catching new features include  flash movies, image rotators, interactive product areas and downloadable wallpapers to encourage user engagement and participation. \r\n\r\nTOG24 also challenged Shark! to improve sales on their existing e-commerce store. Traffic to the site was good but conversion of browsers to purchasers was an area where we felt we could help. \r\n\r\nBased on our research and using our in-house studio, we were commissioned to photograph the latest Winter range. The result - a much improved product image gallery including more detailed shots targetting their outdoor savvy browsers.\r\n\r\nThis new photography, combined with more informative product descriptions helped increase TOG 24’s online winter sales considerably. \r\n\r\nWhat the client said:\r\n\r\n“It was great working with Shark, they identified and made improvements to our site, and the percentage sales increase spoke for itself.”\r\n\r\n*Launch the site here <a href="http://www.tog24.com" title="TOG 24 Website" target="_blank" >TOG24</a>*\r\n', '	<p><span class="caps">TOG</span> 24 appointed Shark! to design and develop their new brand website. The brief: to create a site that reflects the new brand essence (Discover Freedom) and promotes the exciting new winter range&#8230;&#8230;in just 6 weeks.</p>\n\n	<p>The new site launched on time and on budget. Eye-catching new features include  flash movies, image rotators, interactive product areas and downloadable wallpapers to encourage user engagement and participation. </p>\n\n	<p>TOG24 also challenged Shark! to improve sales on their existing e-commerce store. Traffic to the site was good but conversion of browsers to purchasers was an area where we felt we could help. </p>\n\n	<p>Based on our research and using our in-house studio, we were commissioned to photograph the latest Winter range. The result &#8211; a much improved product image gallery including more detailed shots targetting their outdoor savvy browsers.</p>\n\n	<p>This new photography, combined with more informative product descriptions helped increase <span class="caps">TOG</span> 24’s online winter sales considerably. </p>\n\n	<p>What the client said:</p>\n\n	<p>“It was great working with Shark, they identified and made improvements to our site, and the percentage sales increase spoke for itself.”</p>\n\n	<p><strong>Launch the site here <a href="http://www.tog24.com" title="TOG 24 Website" target="_blank" >TOG24</a></strong></p>', 'TOG 24 appoint Shark! to design and develop their new brand website...', '	<p><span class="caps">TOG</span> 24 appoint Shark! to design and develop their new brand website&#8230;</p>', '113,114,115,116,112', 'Digital', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'tog-24', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'bce8d9d60b1d14eee64cddb453a58028', '2008-11-02'),
(83, '2008-10-01 12:06:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2009-04-27 10:41:31', 'andrew', 'TOG 24 appoint Shark Design', '', 'TOG 24 have appointed shark to design and develop their new brand website. The new site is being created to communicate the new brand essence - Discover Freedom, and to better showcase their new ski and boarding range. \r\n\r\nShark design were appointed because of their digital expertise, and ability to deliver the project on budget and on schedule. \r\n\r\nThe site is due to go live in November. \r\n', '	<p><span class="caps">TOG</span> 24 have appointed shark to design and develop their new brand website. The new site is being created to communicate the new brand essence &#8211; Discover Freedom, and to better showcase their new ski and boarding range. </p>\n\n	<p>Shark design were appointed because of their digital expertise, and ability to deliver the project on budget and on schedule. </p>\n\n	<p>The site is due to go live in November. </p>', 'TOG 24 have appointed Shark to design and develop their new brand website.....', '	<p><span class="caps">TOG</span> 24 have appointed Shark to design and develop their new brand website&#8230;..</p>', '106', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'tog-24-appoint-shark-design', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '4faefd004f6467080a67679209b225d3', '2008-11-20');
