(74, '2008-07-15 15:48:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2008-11-02 15:57:27', 'kevin', 'Shark! Curry Club - Latest Scores!', '', 'We''re passionate about what we do at Shark! and we''re equally passionate about a good curry!. The Shark! curry club is going to be touring suitable Yorkshire curry houses and scoring them vigorously with ten being the highest score possible. Not quite A.A.Gill, but a good marker none the less.\r\n\r\nOur latest meal at the Samarkand posted the lowest scores yet (much to Doug''s disgust as it''s his local!) and sits at the bottom of our league table.\r\n\r\nHere are the scores on the board:\r\n\r\n1. Akbahrs           8.25\r\n\r\n2. Balooshi           7.25\r\n\r\n3. Tamana''s          6.20\r\n\r\n4. Samakhand      5.08\r\n\r\nFeel free to get in touch and suggest any venues.', '	<p>We&#8217;re passionate about what we do at Shark! and we&#8217;re equally passionate about a good curry!. The Shark! curry club is going to be touring suitable Yorkshire curry houses and scoring them vigorously with ten being the highest score possible. Not quite A.A.Gill, but a good marker none the less.</p>\n\n	<p>Our latest meal at the Samarkand posted the lowest scores yet (much to Doug&#8217;s disgust as it&#8217;s his local!) and sits at the bottom of our league table.</p>\n\n	<p>Here are the scores on the board:</p>\n\n	<p>1. Akbahrs           8.25</p>\n\n	<p>2. Balooshi           7.25</p>\n\n	<p>3. Tamana&#8217;s          6.20</p>\n\n	<p>4. Samakhand      5.08</p>\n\n	<p>Feel free to get in touch and suggest any venues.</p>', 'We''re passionate about what we do at Shark! and we''re equally passionate about a good curry!...', '	<p>We&#8217;re passionate about what we do at Shark! and we&#8217;re equally passionate about a good curry!&#8230;</p>', '103', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-curry-club-latest-scores', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'b21a0454deb7db3498a5aab9e0c33f16', '2008-11-02'),
(75, '2008-07-03 15:49:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2011-08-16 11:21:04', 'andrew', 'Gateways Goes Live!', '', 'After winning the three way pitch only 8 weeks earlier the pressure was on to go live with the new Gateways School website at the end of term exhibition day on 3rd July. Never ones to miss a deadline, Shark! launched the site in front of the Headmistress, Chairman of Governors and hundreds of guests on a huge screen - possibly the biggest website we''ve ever seen!\r\n\r\nPhotography for the site was also provided by Shark! and excited pupils were soon trying to spot themselves on the new site!\r\n\r\nHave a look at the new site at "www.gatewaysschool.co.uk":http://www.gatewaysschool.co.uk', '	<p>After winning the three way pitch only 8 weeks earlier the pressure was on to go live with the new Gateways School website at the end of term exhibition day on 3rd July. Never ones to miss a deadline, Shark! launched the site in front of the Headmistress, Chairman of Governors and hundreds of guests on a huge screen &#8211; possibly the biggest website we&#8217;ve ever seen!</p>\n\n	<p>Photography for the site was also provided by Shark! and excited pupils were soon trying to spot themselves on the new site!</p>\n\n	<p>Have a look at the new site at <a href="http://www.gatewaysschool.co.uk">www.gatewaysschool.co.uk</a></p>', 'After winning the three way pitch only 8 weeks earlier the pressure was on to go live with the new Gateways School website at the end of term exhibition day on 3rd July...', '	<p>After winning the three way pitch only 8 weeks earlier the pressure was on to go live with the new Gateways School website at the end of term exhibition day on 3rd July&#8230;</p>', '102', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'gateways-goes-live', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'ec971ef47330efeb5aa965c9a73ec742', '2008-11-02'),
(76, '2008-05-02 15:50:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2008-11-02 15:55:05', 'kevin', 'Shark! win Gateways School website pitch', '', 'Shark! are delighted to be working with Gateways School to design and develop their new website. After a three way pitch we were awarded the project as the school felt our design best reflected the "traditional yet innovative" ethos of the school.\r\n\r\nThe large scale of the site required us to develop a unique ''accordian'' style menu to keep navigation clear and intuitive. Our visual content management system will allow the school to keep the site up to date with all the latest news and up coming events and our student blog is sure to be a hit with the pupils.\r\n\r\nNow it''s heads down to meet the challenging deadline of launching the new site live in front of the Headmistress and guests at the Gateways School Exhibition Day on 3rd July!', '	<p>Shark! are delighted to be working with Gateways School to design and develop their new website. After a three way pitch we were awarded the project as the school felt our design best reflected the &#8220;traditional yet innovative&#8221; ethos of the school.</p>\n\n	<p>The large scale of the site required us to develop a unique &#8216;accordian&#8217; style menu to keep navigation clear and intuitive. Our visual content management system will allow the school to keep the site up to date with all the latest news and up coming events and our student blog is sure to be a hit with the pupils.</p>\n\n	<p>Now it&#8217;s heads down to meet the challenging deadline of launching the new site live in front of the Headmistress and guests at the Gateways School Exhibition Day on 3rd July!</p>', 'Shark! are delighted to be working with Gateways School to design and develop their new website...', '	<p>Shark! are delighted to be working with Gateways School to design and develop their new website&#8230;</p>', '101', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-win-gateways-school-website-pitch', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '895f5912cfd3d97e3d165f71e23241eb', '2008-11-02'),
(77, '2008-09-01 16:08:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2009-11-19 17:22:38', 'Andrew', 'Waddington &amp; Ledger', '', 'W&L needed a total overhaul of their brand without losing the integrity of their 100 year old identity. We came up with a creative strategy that used the existing logo in a way that reflected this forward thinking print company''s latest direction. We delivered a complete brand solution including an innovative website, stationery and successful email campaign as well as creating two other sub brands aimed at different sectors of the market. \r\n\r\n*Click here to launch the website – <a href="http://www.wlprint.co.uk" title="W&L Website" target="_blank" >Waddington & Ledger</a>*\r\n', '	<p>W&amp;L needed a total overhaul of their brand without losing the integrity of their 100 year old identity. We came up with a creative strategy that used the existing logo in a way that reflected this forward thinking print company&#8217;s latest direction. We delivered a complete brand solution including an innovative website, stationery and successful email campaign as well as creating two other sub brands aimed at different sectors of the market. </p>\n\n	<p><strong>Click here to launch the website – <a href="http://www.wlprint.co.uk" title="W&L Website" target="_blank" >Waddington &amp; Ledger</a></strong></p>', 'W&L needed a total overhaul of their brand without losing the integrity of their 100 year old identity...', '	<p>W&amp;L needed a total overhaul of their brand without losing the integrity of their 100 year old identity&#8230;</p>', '117,118,119,120,121', 'Digital', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'waddington-ledger', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '330de0da4a1392d67f572ea7ee764bbf', '2008-11-02'),
(78, '2008-11-02 17:41:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2011-03-07 17:32:52', 'andrew', 'Websites', '', 'Helping our clients improve their online presence is what we''re about. We design and build both static and content managed websites with a purpose. Good coding, ease of navigation and Search Engine Optimisation (SEO) are fundamental features of every website we create. We make sure the browser has a reason to keep coming back to your site. \r\n\r\nNever ones to stand on our laurels we''re always exploring innovative techniques to use whether it''s Flash, Java Script or simple HTML.\r\n\r\nAll our sites are developed using best practice techniques conforming to the latest World Wide Web Consortium (W3C) standards.', '	<p>Helping our clients improve their online presence is what we&#8217;re about. We design and build both static and content managed websites with a purpose. Good coding, ease of navigation and Search Engine Optimisation (<span class="caps">SEO</span>) are fundamental features of every website we create. We make sure the browser has a reason to keep coming back to your site. </p>\n\n	<p>Never ones to stand on our laurels we&#8217;re always exploring innovative techniques to use whether it&#8217;s Flash, Java Script or simple <span class="caps">HTML</span>.</p>\n\n	<p>All our sites are developed using best practice techniques conforming to the latest World Wide Web Consortium (W3C) standards.</p>', '', '', '', 'Websites', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'what-we-do', '', '', 'websites', '10', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'f5488aef770805c10bb891748e760f4c', '2008-11-02'),
(79, '2008-11-02 17:42:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2008-11-02 17:43:13', '', 'E-Commerce', '', 'Our E-Commerce sites are always built bespoke. We don''t re-skin sites built for other people and only after we fully understand your business and identify your target audience will we begin to create a site that will work specifically for you. From a simple subscription site, to a huge online store, our aim is to make it as easy as possible for customers to make a purchase and for the client to update and maintain their website.', '	<p>Our E-Commerce sites are always built bespoke. We don&#8217;t re-skin sites built for other people and only after we fully understand your business and identify your target audience will we begin to create a site that will work specifically for you. From a simple subscription site, to a huge online store, our aim is to make it as easy as possible for customers to make a purchase and for the client to update and maintain their website.</p>', '', '', '', 'E-Commerce', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'what-we-do', '', '', 'e-commerce', '11', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '2e155147b613d580d20b5e0b267a85d9', '2008-11-02'),
(80, '2008-11-02 17:43:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2008-11-02 17:44:00', '', 'Search Engine Optimisation', '', 'We always build our sites with good SEO in mind as well as working on existing sites where natural/organic search needs improving. We understand the algorithms that search engines employ to rank sites and we always use search engine friendly coding. SEO (natural or Pay per Click) should always be treated as an ongoing project, major search engines can change how they rank sites in a heartbeat, so you need to be able to respond quickly.', '	<p>We always build our sites with good <span class="caps">SEO</span> in mind as well as working on existing sites where natural/organic search needs improving. We understand the algorithms that search engines employ to rank sites and we always use search engine friendly coding. <span class="caps">SEO</span> (natural or Pay per Click) should always be treated as an ongoing project, major search engines can change how they rank sites in a heartbeat, so you need to be able to respond quickly.</p>', '', '', '', 'Search-Engine-Optimisation', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'what-we-do', '', '', 'search-engine-optimisation', '12', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '6f6620d83f79daf35bcd61c0fe1896e6', '2008-11-02'),
(81, '2008-11-02 17:44:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2013-08-09 11:25:59', 'andrew', 'E-mail', '', 'Often overlooked, email marketing is a cost effective way of driving sales, learning more about your customers, creating awareness and building loyalty for any business, of any size, in any sector. What''s more it''s measurable and can be highly targetted too.\r\n\r\nWith consumers connecting to email several times a day on their mobile devices it''s vital to be where your customers are and email enables you to be there quickly.\r\n\r\nMany digital specialists lack the direct marketing skills to take full advantage of this tool so why not give us a call and let us demonstrate how we can help you. \r\n', '	<p>Often overlooked, email marketing is a cost effective way of driving sales, learning more about your customers, creating awareness and building loyalty for any business, of any size, in any sector. What&#8217;s more it&#8217;s measurable and can be highly targetted too.</p>\n\n	<p>With consumers connecting to email several times a day on their mobile devices it&#8217;s vital to be where your customers are and email enables you to be there quickly.</p>\n\n	<p>Many digital specialists lack the direct marketing skills to take full advantage of this tool so why not give us a call and let us demonstrate how we can help you. </p>', '', '', '', 'Email', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'what-we-do', '', '', 'e-mail', '13', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'ccb78ce1573c84ed9212f30be0f52663', '2008-11-02'),
(84, '2008-11-14 14:32:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2013-08-09 10:08:31', 'andrew', 'Dugdale Bros new website goes live', '', 'Shark Design recently launched the new website for Huddersfield based Dugdale Bros & Co. Dugdale, who have a long and rich tradition in the cloth industry, needed a website to reflect their heritage and promote their latest range of products. We provided design, photography and web development. \r\n\r\nTo view the Dugdale site, "click here":http://www.dugdalebros.com\r\n\r\n', '	<p>Shark Design recently launched the new website for Huddersfield based Dugdale Bros &amp; Co. Dugdale, who have a long and rich tradition in the cloth industry, needed a website to reflect their heritage and promote their latest range of products. We provided design, photography and web development. </p>\n\n	<p>To view the Dugdale site, <a href="http://www.dugdalebros.com">click here</a></p>', 'Shark Design recently launched the new website for Huddersfield based Dugdale Bros & Co...', '	<p>Shark Design recently launched the new website for Huddersfield based Dugdale Bros &amp; Co&#8230;</p>', '107', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'dugdale-bros-new-website-goes-live', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'd2783113e375e0fb937a644cb7005b48', '2008-11-20'),
(85, '2008-10-15 14:12:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2013-08-09 09:56:22', 'andrew', 'Shark! Curry Club goes Thai', '', 'The Shark! club has gone slightly off brief this month. We''ve been out for a Thai curry. The venue was Puja Thai in Lindley, Huddersfield. \r\n\r\nPuja Thai went down pretty well and scored highly with an average of 8.1. \r\n\r\nHere are the latest scores on the board:\r\n\r\n1. Akbahrs - 8.25\r\n\r\n2. Puja Thai - 8.1\r\n\r\n3. Balooshi - 7.25\r\n\r\n4. Tamana''s - 6.20\r\n\r\n5. Samakhand - 5.08', '	<p>The Shark! club has gone slightly off brief this month. We&#8217;ve been out for a Thai curry. The venue was Puja Thai in Lindley, Huddersfield. </p>\n\n	<p>Puja Thai went down pretty well and scored highly with an average of 8.1. </p>\n\n	<p>Here are the latest scores on the board:</p>\n\n	<p>1. Akbahrs &#8211; 8.25</p>\n\n	<p>2. Puja Thai &#8211; 8.1</p>\n\n	<p>3. Balooshi &#8211; 7.25</p>\n\n	<p>4. Tamana&#8217;s &#8211; 6.20</p>\n\n	<p>5. Samakhand &#8211; 5.08</p>', 'The Shark! club has gone slightly off brief this month. We''ve been out for a Thai curry.', '	<p>The Shark! club has gone slightly off brief this month. We&#8217;ve been out for a Thai curry.</p>', '103', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-curry-club-goes-thai', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0770e7bf84cf59f1f4ceed4458b15f5b', '2008-11-20'),
(86, '2008-10-30 14:25:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2011-09-09 11:25:51', 'andrew', 'Matthew joins the Shark team', '', 'Matthew Ogden has joined Shark to work on business development. He will be responsible for attracting new clients and developing existing accounts.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n ', '	<p>Matthew Ogden has joined Shark to work on business development. He will be responsible for attracting new clients and developing existing accounts.</p>\n\n ', 'Matthew Ogden has joined the shark team.....', '	<p>Matthew Ogden has joined the shark team&#8230;..</p>', '110', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'matthew-joins-the-shark-team', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'd63f857843c11f67c842b8ae83f59135', '2008-11-20'),
(87, '2008-11-10 14:31:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2008-12-03 16:25:17', 'andrew', 'Shark launch new Swimbabes e-commerce site', '', 'Following the re-brand of Swimbabes earlier in the year, Shark are pleased to announce the launch of their new e-commerce store. \r\n\r\nThe new online store was designed and developed to increase conversion rates, improve natural Search Engine Optimisation (SEO) and allow the easy measurement of Return on Investment (ROI) on all promotional campaigns. The site is fully content manageable and has stock management capability.\r\n\r\nSwimbabes have also appointed Shark Design & Marketing to work on SEO on a monthly basis. \r\n\r\nVisit the new store "here":http://www.swimbabes.co.uk\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '	<p>Following the re-brand of Swimbabes earlier in the year, Shark are pleased to announce the launch of their new e-commerce store. </p>\n\n	<p>The new online store was designed and developed to increase conversion rates, improve natural Search Engine Optimisation (<span class="caps">SEO</span>) and allow the easy measurement of Return on Investment (<span class="caps">ROI</span>) on all promotional campaigns. The site is fully content manageable and has stock management capability.</p>\n\n	<p>Swimbabes have also appointed Shark Design &amp; Marketing to work on <span class="caps">SEO</span> on a monthly basis. </p>\n\n	<p>Visit the new store <a href="http://www.swimbabes.co.uk">here</a></p>\n\n', 'Following the re-brand of Swimbabes earlier in the year, Shark are pleased to announce ......', '	<p>Following the re-brand of Swimbabes earlier in the year, Shark are pleased to announce &#8230;&#8230;</p>', '109', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-launch-new-swimbabes-e-commerce-site', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'fd7fa5ed6cd092c0a47bb3c56017e1e5', '2008-11-20'),
(88, '2008-11-17 15:10:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2013-08-09 10:00:43', 'andrew', 'Shark Design launch TOG 24 brand site', '', 'TOG24’s new brand website launched in mid November, on time and on budget. Set the challenge of reflecting the new brand essence of ‘Discover Freedom’ and promoting the exciting new winter range, Shark designed and developed the site within six weeks of the initial brief. \r\n\r\nEye catching features include flash movies, image rotators, an interactive product area and dowloadable wallpapers.\r\n\r\nShark designed and developed the new site through intelligent use of java script and php. The site has a real “Flash” feel without having to rely heavily on that technology. This means that all the text is live which is beneficial to natural SEO.\r\n\r\nView the new site here - "TOG 24":http://www.tog24.com', '	<p>TOG24’s new brand website launched in mid November, on time and on budget. Set the challenge of reflecting the new brand essence of ‘Discover Freedom’ and promoting the exciting new winter range, Shark designed and developed the site within six weeks of the initial brief. </p>\n\n	<p>Eye catching features include flash movies, image rotators, an interactive product area and dowloadable wallpapers.</p>\n\n	<p>Shark designed and developed the new site through intelligent use of java script and php. The site has a real “Flash” feel without having to rely heavily on that technology. This means that all the text is live which is beneficial to natural <span class="caps">SEO</span>.</p>\n\n	<p>View the new site here &#8211; <a href="http://www.tog24.com"><span class="caps">TOG</span> 24</a></p>', 'TOG24’s new brand site launched in mid November, on time and on budget. ', '	<p>TOG24’s new brand site launched in mid November, on time and on budget. </p>', '106', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-design-launchtog24-brand-site', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'b065beca16863e85714fbae4e2582924', '2008-11-20'),
(89, '2008-11-20 15:34:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2009-04-27 10:40:28', 'andrew', 'Shark Design win London pitch', '', 'Shark Design recently won a 3-way pitch against London agencies for the Sue Ryder ‘Lights of Love - Book of Celebration’ campaign. The brief included designing a book and mail pack capable of holding 35,000 names that would be considered a fitting tribute by their donors. Working within tight budget constraints Shark were appointed based on a number of factors including creative flair and interpretation of the brief plus our direct mail and production expertise.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n', '	<p>Shark Design recently won a 3-way pitch against London agencies for the Sue Ryder ‘Lights of Love &#8211; Book of Celebration’ campaign. The brief included designing a book and mail pack capable of holding 35,000 names that would be considered a fitting tribute by their donors. Working within tight budget constraints Shark were appointed based on a number of factors including creative flair and interpretation of the brief plus our direct mail and production expertise.</p>\n\n', 'Shark Design win 3 way pitch for London charity Sue Ryder Care.', '	<p>Shark Design win 3 way pitch for London charity Sue Ryder Care.</p>', '111', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-design-win-london-pitch', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '1759f4c1dfcbeaa2ae8ab9695f3082a7', '2008-11-20'),
(90, '2009-01-20 11:52:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Andrew', '2009-01-20 12:20:52', 'andrew', 'Shark Design answers Green SOS!', '', 'When Gateways School was selected from hundreds of entries to become a finalist in npowers’ national ‘Climate Cops Green SOS Programme’ (their idea – to knit strong reusable carrier bags, and socks for mobile phones and iPods from old plastic bags and stockings) – they needed a brand identity to reflect their values and be instantly recognisable in their local community and beyond.\r\n\r\nAlways happy to support environmental and community programmes, Shark designed several logo ideas for use across stationery, clothing and label tags. \r\n\r\nSoon after, the ‘GreenStitch’ brand was born!\r\n\r\nI am sure you will join everyone at Shark in congratulating the GreenStitch team in their achievements and efforts in helping save our planet ‘one stitch at a time’.\r\n\r\nGood luck in the final girls!\r\n', '	<p>When Gateways School was selected from hundreds of entries to become a finalist in npowers’ national ‘Climate Cops Green <span class="caps">SOS</span> Programme’ (their idea – to knit strong reusable carrier bags, and socks for mobile phones and iPods from old plastic bags and stockings) – they needed a brand identity to reflect their values and be instantly recognisable in their local community and beyond.</p>\n\n	<p>Always happy to support environmental and community programmes, Shark designed several logo ideas for use across stationery, clothing and label tags. </p>\n\n	<p>Soon after, the ‘GreenStitch’ brand was born!</p>\n\n	<p>I am sure you will join everyone at Shark in congratulating the GreenStitch team in their achievements and efforts in helping save our planet ‘one stitch at a time’.</p>\n\n	<p>Good luck in the final girls!</p>', 'When Gateways School was selected from hundreds of entries to become a finalist in npowers’ national ‘Climate Cops Green SOS Programme’ ...', '	<p>When Gateways School was selected from hundreds of entries to become a finalist in npowers’ national ‘Climate Cops Green <span class="caps">SOS</span> Programme’ &#8230;</p>', '122', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-design-answers-green-sos', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '02c51ba5e301c71ee4d6db2b479034d0', '2009-01-20'),
(91, '2009-01-28 11:08:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2013-08-09 10:00:20', 'andrew', 'Shark Design has moved!', '', 'We considered New York but it’s a tricky commute – especially for Doug on his scooter!\r\n\r\nOn a serious note though, we are delighted to announce that we recently moved to cracking new offices. \r\n\r\nWe look forward to seeing you soon and please don’t forget to update your records with our new address:\r\n\r\nThe Waddington & Ledger Building\r\nLowfields Way\r\nElland\r\nWest Yorkshire\r\nHX5 9DA\r\n\r\nP.S. Special thanks to John for mounting our company mascot Bruce (not literally of course!)  \r\n', '	<p>We considered New York but it’s a tricky commute – especially for Doug on his scooter!</p>\n\n	<p>On a serious note though, we are delighted to announce that we recently moved to cracking new offices. </p>\n\n	<p>We look forward to seeing you soon and please don’t forget to update your records with our new address:</p>\n\n	<p>The Waddington &amp; Ledger Building<br />\nLowfields Way<br />\nElland<br />\nWest Yorkshire<br />\nHX5 9DA</p>\n\n	<p>P.S. Special thanks to John for mounting our company mascot Bruce (not literally of course!)  </p>', 'We considered New York but it’s a tricky commute – especially for Doug on his scooter!', '	<p>We considered New York but it’s a tricky commute – especially for Doug on his scooter!</p>', '123', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-design-has-moved', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '12b14c5e9014a27a109fe0f14ada7b39', '2009-01-28'),
(92, '2009-03-15 11:23:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2013-08-09 09:59:59', 'andrew', 'Towngate Plc', '', 'Shark Design & Marketing were  appointed by Towngate PLC - one of the North of England’s leading commercial and industrial property specialists – to design and develop their new website.\r\n\r\nRather than us telling you what this involved and how it has helped their business, why not hear it from Towngate direct:\r\n\r\n"I appointed Shark to design a user friendly, easy to navigate, attractive website to replace our existing, rather tired and complicated one.  They listened to my quite extensive brief and subsequently lived and breathed Towngate for several weeks in order to gain a greater understanding of the activities of the Towngate Group, the messages / information we need to give to our existing and potential tenants /customers, along with their requirements.  The knowledge they gained has translated into a great site, with simple to use navigation tools and information features.  The branding / colours used reflect our rather colourful firebird logo and create a very attractive, enjoyable web experience.  The site went live at the end of January 2009 and I have received some extremely positive feedback, and furthermore - business - which the previous site failed to do! Visits to the site have increased significantly and Shark continue to offer great support now that the content of the site is managed by ourselves in-house".\r\n\r\nJulia Ford, Marketing Manager, Towngate Plc\r\n\r\n*Launch the site here - <a href="http://www.towngate.plc.uk" title="Towngate Website" target="_blank" >Towngate</a>*\r\n\r\nP.S. We were also asked to update Towngate’s availability catalogue and newsletter to make them consistent with the style of their new website. \r\n', '	<p>Shark Design &amp; Marketing were  appointed by Towngate <span class="caps">PLC</span> &#8211; one of the North of England’s leading commercial and industrial property specialists – to design and develop their new website.</p>\n\n	<p>Rather than us telling you what this involved and how it has helped their business, why not hear it from Towngate direct:</p>\n\n	<p>&#8220;I appointed Shark to design a user friendly, easy to navigate, attractive website to replace our existing, rather tired and complicated one.  They listened to my quite extensive brief and subsequently lived and breathed Towngate for several weeks in order to gain a greater understanding of the activities of the Towngate Group, the messages / information we need to give to our existing and potential tenants /customers, along with their requirements.  The knowledge they gained has translated into a great site, with simple to use navigation tools and information features.  The branding / colours used reflect our rather colourful firebird logo and create a very attractive, enjoyable web experience.  The site went live at the end of January 2009 and I have received some extremely positive feedback, and furthermore &#8211; business &#8211; which the previous site failed to do! Visits to the site have increased significantly and Shark continue to offer great support now that the content of the site is managed by ourselves in-house&#8221;.</p>\n\n	<p>Julia Ford, Marketing Manager, Towngate Plc</p>\n\n	<p><strong>Launch the site here &#8211; <a href="http://www.towngate.plc.uk" title="Towngate Website" target="_blank" >Towngate</a></strong></p>\n\n	<p>P.S. We were also asked to update Towngate’s availability catalogue and newsletter to make them consistent with the style of their new website. </p>', 'Shark Design & Marketing were appointed by Towngate PLC to design and develop their new website.', '	<p>Shark Design &amp; Marketing were appointed by Towngate <span class="caps">PLC</span> to design and develop their new website.</p>', '124,125,126,127,128', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'towngate-plc', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'fc76af252827d21cb2bd63728a336faf', '2009-04-15'),
(93, '2009-02-15 11:38:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2013-08-09 10:04:55', 'andrew', 'Shark Design launch Towngate Plc site', '', 'Shark Design & Marketing were recently appointed by Towngate PLC - one of the North of England’s leading commercial and industrial property developers – to design and develop their new content managed (CMS) website. \r\n\r\nWe were asked to create an attractive, user friendly website that showcases towgates properties and services to potential tenants. \r\n\r\nThe new site launched in January, "Click here to launch the website":http://www.towngate.plc.uk\r\n\r\n"View the case study by clicking here":/case-studies/towngate-plc\r\n\r\nSince the launch we''ve been working with a delighted Towngate to update all their marketing literature so that it''s consistent with the new website. ', '	<p>Shark Design &amp; Marketing were recently appointed by Towngate <span class="caps">PLC</span> &#8211; one of the North of England’s leading commercial and industrial property developers – to design and develop their new content managed (<span class="caps">CMS</span>) website. </p>\n\n	<p>We were asked to create an attractive, user friendly website that showcases towgates properties and services to potential tenants. </p>\n\n	<p>The new site launched in January, <a href="http://www.towngate.plc.uk">Click here to launch the website</a></p>\n\n	<p><a href="/case-studies/towngate-plc">View the case study by clicking here</a></p>\n\n	<p>Since the launch we&#8217;ve been working with a delighted Towngate to update all their marketing literature so that it&#8217;s consistent with the new website. </p>', 'Shark Design & Marketing were recently appointed by Towngate PLC to design and develop their new content managed (CMS) website. ', '	<p>Shark Design &amp; Marketing were recently appointed by Towngate <span class="caps">PLC</span> to design and develop their new content managed (<span class="caps">CMS</span>) website. </p>', '124', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', 'test', 'shark-design-launch-towngate-plc-site', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'ef8ddce88f5c5a592cbab5868ed50a2f', '2009-04-15'),
(94, '2009-02-14 16:58:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2009-04-20 17:02:23', 'andrew', 'Sue Ryder Care - Lights Of Love', '', 'Shark Design recently won a 3-way pitch for national charity Sue Ryder Care. \r\n\r\nTheir ‘Lights of Love – Book of Celebration’ brief included designing a fitting tribute containing the names of 12,000 loved-ones lost. \r\n\r\nShark created and produced a ‘keepsake’ book with die-cut bookmark enabling donors to mark the page where friends or relatives names appeared. \r\n\r\nMailing on time and under budget the Book of Celebration pack was a great success, exceeding the clients’ target response rate for direct debit donors\r\n', '	<p>Shark Design recently won a 3-way pitch for national charity Sue Ryder Care. </p>\n\n	<p>Their ‘Lights of Love – Book of Celebration’ brief included designing a fitting tribute containing the names of 12,000 loved-ones lost. </p>\n\n	<p>Shark created and produced a ‘keepsake’ book with die-cut bookmark enabling donors to mark the page where friends or relatives names appeared. </p>\n\n	<p>Mailing on time and under budget the Book of Celebration pack was a great success, exceeding the clients’ target response rate for direct debit donors</p>', 'Shark Design recently won a 3-way pitch for national charity Sue Ryder Care. ', '	<p>Shark Design recently won a 3-way pitch for national charity Sue Ryder Care. </p>', '129,130,131,132,133', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'sue-ryder-care-lights-of-love', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '40b07647f81d90a7b6e89dfddac6293a', '2009-04-20'),
(95, '2009-04-20 17:06:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2011-09-09 11:27:35', 'andrew', 'Shark! curry club goes to Leenas', '', 'After a few months burning off the excess Xmas calories (We''re all still following a strict diet religiously - <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1NjTWvl8x-U" target="_blank" >Click Here To See The Video</a>) the Shark! curry club is back. We selected Leenas in Lindley, Huddersfield, for our first outing of ‘09.  \r\n\r\nThe food was very good and Leenas scored an average of 7.4, which puts it in 3rd place on the leader board. \r\n\r\n1. Akbahrs – 8.25\r\n2. Puja Thai – 8.1\r\n3. Leenas – 7.4\r\n3. Balooshi – 7.25\r\n4. Tamana’s – 6.20\r\n5. Samakhand – 5.08\r\n\r\nWill any curry house ever be worse than Doug’s selection, Samakhand? Lee is making us all go to a veggie place next… let’s see how that goes down. \r\n', '	<p>After a few months burning off the excess Xmas calories (We&#8217;re all still following a strict diet religiously &#8211; <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1NjTWvl8x-U" target="_blank" >Click Here To See The Video</a>) the Shark! curry club is back. We selected Leenas in Lindley, Huddersfield, for our first outing of ‘09.  </p>\n\n	<p>The food was very good and Leenas scored an average of 7.4, which puts it in 3rd place on the leader board. </p>\n\n	<p>1. Akbahrs – 8.25<br />\n2. Puja Thai – 8.1<br />\n3. Leenas – 7.4<br />\n3. Balooshi – 7.25<br />\n4. Tamana’s – 6.20<br />\n5. Samakhand – 5.08</p>\n\n	<p>Will any curry house ever be worse than Doug’s selection, Samakhand? Lee is making us all go to a veggie place next… let’s see how that goes down. </p>', 'After a few months burning off the excess Xmas calories the Shark! curry club is back. ', '	<p>After a few months burning off the excess Xmas calories the Shark! curry club is back. </p>', '134', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-curry-club-goes-to-leenas', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'bef6f825659591c1aeba90b41171aafa', '2009-04-20'),
(97, '2009-05-03 17:32:03', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Andrew', '2013-08-09 09:59:22', 'andrew', 'Shark design Cumbria Tourism awards', '', 'We were delighted to be involved with the latest Cumbria Tourism awards night. As we have produced work for the region throughout the year it was particularly pleasing to be asked to support the event. \r\n\r\nWe designed and produced a full suite of material for the project. Cumbria Tourism were delighted with results, commenting: <strong>“The programme, signage and powerpoint looked great on the night and really helped to make the event professional and slick”</strong>\r\n', '	<p>We were delighted to be involved with the latest Cumbria Tourism awards night. As we have produced work for the region throughout the year it was particularly pleasing to be asked to support the event. </p>\n\n	<p>We designed and produced a full suite of material for the project. Cumbria Tourism were delighted with results, commenting: <strong>“The programme, signage and powerpoint looked great on the night and really helped to make the event professional and slick”</strong></p>', 'We were delighted to be involved with the latest Cumbria Tourism awards night...', '	<p>We were delighted to be involved with the latest Cumbria Tourism awards night&#8230;</p>', '41', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-design-cumbria-tourism-awards', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '38acca7990a04672d3d6c7fa6156388e', '2009-06-03'),
(116, '2011-08-16 11:36:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2011-08-16 11:36:26', 'andrew', 'Radio Rastrick', '', 'When, as part of their media studies course, the pupils at Rastrick High School & Sixth Form College started their own school radio station Shark Design were delighted to work with them to develop their own unique identity. Take a look at their new logo here. ', '	<p>When, as part of their media studies course, the pupils at Rastrick High School &amp; Sixth Form College started their own school radio station Shark Design were delighted to work with them to develop their own unique identity. Take a look at their new logo here. </p>', 'When, as part of their media studies course, the pupils at Rastrick High School & Sixth Form College started their own school radio station', '	<p>When, as part of their media studies course, the pupils at Rastrick High School &amp; Sixth Form College started their own school radio station</p>', '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'radio-rastrick', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'd602356b1bfbc8283c1fcea322daeda2', '2010-07-15'),
(98, '2009-06-01 17:55:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Andrew', '2009-06-05 13:26:32', 'Andrew', 'Shark Design appointed by M&amp;Co.', '', 'Although there are still 204 shopping days to go, Christmas has already started for us! \r\n\r\nFashion retailer M&Co. has appointed Shark! Design & Marketing to create the window POS for their most important campaign of the year – Christmas.\r\n\r\nShark and production partners, "Kuhnel":http://www.kuhnel.co.uk/pages/index.html, will be providing POS for all 290 UK stores. \r\n\r\nM&Co. have been delighted with the Shark-Kuhnel partnership, saying…<strong>”You’ve met all expectations and it has certainly been one of our easiest Christmas sign off''s”</strong>. \r\n\r\nThe campaign promises to be innovative, striking and illuminating…so watch this space!\r\n', '	<p>Although there are still 204 shopping days to go, Christmas has already started for us! </p>\n\n	<p>Fashion retailer M&amp;Co. has appointed Shark! Design &amp; Marketing to create the window <span class="caps">POS</span> for their most important campaign of the year – Christmas.</p>\n\n	<p>Shark and production partners, <a href="http://www.kuhnel.co.uk/pages/index.html">Kuhnel</a>, will be providing <span class="caps">POS</span> for all 290 UK stores. </p>\n\n	<p>M&amp;Co. have been delighted with the Shark-Kuhnel partnership, saying…<strong>”You’ve met all expectations and it has certainly been one of our easiest Christmas sign off&#8217;s”</strong>. </p>\n\n	<p>The campaign promises to be innovative, striking and illuminating…so watch this space!</p>', 'Although there are still 204 shopping days to go, Christmas has already started for us! ', '	<p>Although there are still 204 shopping days to go, Christmas has already started for us! </p>', '137', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-design-appointed-by-mco', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'fe796ce8a4a179f32f30886646dc3b7d', '2009-06-03'),
(99, '2009-07-29 16:40:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Andrew', '2014-02-21 11:50:33', 'andrew', 'POS &amp; Packaging', '', 'Shark Design and Marketing are often invited to develop and print Point of Sale (POS) material and creative packaging for retailers and FMCG companies. Stroll down any UK high street or walk through one of the major supermarkets and you’re sure to see our work.\r\n\r\nTake a look at some examples of how we''ve helped create attractive selling environments, packaging with outstanding shelf presence and in-store communication solutions above.\r\n\r\nIf you''re looking for ways to increase sales in-store why not give us a call?', '	<p>Shark Design and Marketing are often invited to develop and print Point of Sale (<span class="caps">POS</span>) material and creative packaging for retailers and <span class="caps">FMCG</span> companies. Stroll down any UK high street or walk through one of the major supermarkets and you’re sure to see our work.</p>\n\n	<p>Take a look at some examples of how we&#8217;ve helped create attractive selling environments, packaging with outstanding shelf presence and in-store communication solutions above.</p>\n\n	<p>If you&#8217;re looking for ways to increase sales in-store why not give us a call?</p>', '', '', '404,412,376,377,413,323,321,311,312,294,267,270,271,242,149,150,175,179,176,178,143,144,142,140,141,138,139', 'pos-packaging', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'portfolio', '', '', 'pos-packaging', '04', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'd7de95d14cc34b81000417522cf587e4', '2009-06-04'),
(100, '2009-06-01 15:24:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Andrew', '2011-09-09 11:26:59', 'andrew', 'Matt &amp; Lee finally make brew!', '', 'After 6 months with Shark Design, Matt has finally agreed to make a round of brews... Let''s hope he gets them right. \r\n\r\n*News Update*...\r\n\r\nIncredibly, on the back of Matthew''s shock brew comes another surprise. After 2 years Lee has finally made the full team a coffee. \r\n\r\n', '	<p>After 6 months with Shark Design, Matt has finally agreed to make a round of brews&#8230; Let&#8217;s hope he gets them right. </p>\n\n	<p><strong>News Update</strong>&#8230;</p>\n\n	<p>Incredibly, on the back of Matthew&#8217;s shock brew comes another surprise. After 2 years Lee has finally made the full team a coffee. </p>\n\n', 'After 6 months with Shark Design, Matt has finally agreed to make a round of brews... Let''s hope he gets them right. ', '	<p>After 6 months with Shark Design, Matt has finally agreed to make a round of brews&#8230; Let&#8217;s hope he gets them right. </p>', '62', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'matt-makes-brew', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '77e0dded653d592d5209bdcff25a4a78', '2009-06-17'),
(101, '2009-09-21 09:52:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Andrew', '2009-10-13 15:42:38', 'andrew', 'The Yorkshire Saucery', '', 'Shark! Design & Marketing created the brand, packaging and website for The Yorkshire Saucery - a new range of chilled fish sauces sold exclusively in ASDA. Communicating the products’ freshness and capturing the expertise and passion needed to make the sauces was vital. By using a brown paper, handwritten font and “I heart” stickers we produced packaging with a handmade, delicatessen feel that is fresh and friendly. \r\n\r\nHere''s what the client thought...\r\n\r\nCreating a brand identity for a range of products to sell exclusively in the world’s largest retailer is a real challenge however Shark understood our brief quickly and captured the brand values creatively and coherently. Their responsiveness enabled us to launch ahead of schedule and what’s more, products are selling well!\r\n\r\n*Launch the site here - <a href="http://www.theyorkshiresaucery.com" title="The Yorkshire Saucery Website" target="_blank" >The Yorkshire Saucery</a>*\r\n\r\nThe Yorkshire Saucery has now been added to Lovely Package, featuring the very best that packaging design has to offer. *Check it out! - <a href="http://lovelypackage.com/the-yorkshire-saucery/#more-8184" title="Lovely Package" target="_blank" >The Yorkshire Saucery on Lovely Package</a>*', '	<p>Shark! Design &amp; Marketing created the brand, packaging and website for The Yorkshire Saucery &#8211; a new range of chilled fish sauces sold exclusively in <span class="caps">ASDA</span>. Communicating the products’ freshness and capturing the expertise and passion needed to make the sauces was vital. By using a brown paper, handwritten font and “I heart” stickers we produced packaging with a handmade, delicatessen feel that is fresh and friendly. </p>\n\n	<p>Here&#8217;s what the client thought&#8230;</p>\n\n	<p>Creating a brand identity for a range of products to sell exclusively in the world’s largest retailer is a real challenge however Shark understood our brief quickly and captured the brand values creatively and coherently. Their responsiveness enabled us to launch ahead of schedule and what’s more, products are selling well!</p>\n\n	<p><strong>Launch the site here &#8211; <a href="http://www.theyorkshiresaucery.com" title="The Yorkshire Saucery Website" target="_blank" >The Yorkshire Saucery</a></strong></p>\n\n	<p>The Yorkshire Saucery has now been added to Lovely Package, featuring the very best that packaging design has to offer. <strong>Check it out! &#8211; <a href="http://lovelypackage.com/the-yorkshire-saucery/#more-8184" title="Lovely Package" target="_blank" >The Yorkshire Saucery on Lovely Package</a></strong></p>', 'Shark! Design & Marketing created the brand, packaging and website for The Yorkshire Saucery ', '	<p>Shark! Design &amp; Marketing created the brand, packaging and website for The Yorkshire Saucery </p>', '151,152,153,154,155', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'the-yorkshire-saucery', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '7780b6f5843d456a23ddcd810de884d3', '2009-09-21'),
(115, '2010-07-15 12:13:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2010-07-15 12:13:46', 'andrew', 'The Yorkshire Saucery – new packaging', '', 'After successfully creating the brand identity for The Yorkshire Saucery – a new range of chilled sauces sold exclusively in ASDA – Shark Design & Marketing were recently tasked with translating the brand across two new forms of packaging. Click here to see our designs for the new multi-pack and individual portion pots.', '	<p>After successfully creating the brand identity for The Yorkshire Saucery – a new range of chilled sauces sold exclusively in <span class="caps">ASDA</span> – Shark Design &amp; Marketing were recently tasked with translating the brand across two new forms of packaging. Click here to see our designs for the new multi-pack and individual portion pots.</p>', 'After successfully creating the brand identity for The Yorkshire Saucery – a new range of chilled sauces sold exclusively in ASDA -', '	<p>After successfully creating the brand identity for The Yorkshire Saucery – a new range of chilled sauces sold exclusively in <span class="caps">ASDA</span> &#8211; </p>', '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'the-yorkshire-saucery-new-packaging', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'e6e362325848c3d353b98eb815813b79', '2010-07-15'),
(103, '2009-09-21 10:28:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Andrew', '2009-10-13 15:56:37', 'andrew', 'Shark Gets Saucy!', '', 'Shark! Design recently created the brand, packaging and website for The Yorkshire Saucery - a new range of chilled fish sauces sold exclusively in ASDA. \r\n\r\n"Click here to view the case study":/case-studies/the-yorkshire-saucery \r\n\r\nP.S. The packaging has now been added to Lovely Package, featuring the very best that packaging design has to offer. *Check it out! - <a href="http://lovelypackage.com/the-yorkshire-saucery/#more-8184" title="Lovely Package" target="_blank" >The Yorkshire Saucery on Lovely Package</a>*', '	<p>Shark! Design recently created the brand, packaging and website for The Yorkshire Saucery &#8211; a new range of chilled fish sauces sold exclusively in <span class="caps">ASDA</span>. </p>\n\n	<p><a href="/case-studies/the-yorkshire-saucery">Click here to view the case study</a> </p>\n\n	<p>P.S. The packaging has now been added to Lovely Package, featuring the very best that packaging design has to offer. <strong>Check it out! &#8211; <a href="http://lovelypackage.com/the-yorkshire-saucery/#more-8184" title="Lovely Package" target="_blank" >The Yorkshire Saucery on Lovely Package</a></strong></p>', 'Shark! Design recently created the brand, packaging and website for The Yorkshire Saucery.', '	<p>Shark! Design recently created the brand, packaging and website for The Yorkshire Saucery.</p>', '150', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-gets-saucy', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'b4a367d989e0a18e19e9431f6a236f55', '2009-09-21');
