(106, '2009-08-30 12:10:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Andrew', '2013-08-09 09:58:59', 'andrew', 'Shark Design comes highly recommended!', '', 'Shark Design & Marketing has been accredited a RAR recommended agency for 2009 – so a big thanks to all who took the time to say what you thought of us!\r\n\r\nIf you didn’t know, RAR confidentially measures an agency''s level of customer satisfaction, asking clients to rate their suppliers across five areas: \r\n\r\n1.         Account management \r\n2.         Creativity \r\n3.         Professionalism \r\n4.         Strategic thinking\r\n5.         Value for money \r\n\r\nWe are delighted to have scored highly across the board. In fact, we scored very highly for value for money, strategic thinking and creativity. \r\n\r\nIf you want to experience any of the above or want to discuss a specific project, please get in touch by calling 01422 375 333, or emailing us at info@sharkdesign.co.uk.\r\n', '	<p>Shark Design &amp; Marketing has been accredited a <span class="caps">RAR</span> recommended agency for 2009 – so a big thanks to all who took the time to say what you thought of us!</p>\n\n	<p>If you didn’t know, <span class="caps">RAR</span> confidentially measures an agency&#8217;s level of customer satisfaction, asking clients to rate their suppliers across five areas: </p>\n\n	<p>1.         Account management <br />\n2.         Creativity <br />\n3.         Professionalism <br />\n4.         Strategic thinking<br />\n5.         Value for money </p>\n\n	<p>We are delighted to have scored highly across the board. In fact, we scored very highly for value for money, strategic thinking and creativity. </p>\n\n	<p>If you want to experience any of the above or want to discuss a specific project, please get in touch by calling 01422 375 333, or emailing us at info@sharkdesign.co.uk.</p>', 'Shark Design & Marketing has been accredited a RAR recommended agency for 2009 ', '	<p>Shark Design &amp; Marketing has been accredited a <span class="caps">RAR</span> recommended agency for 2009 </p>', '159', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-design-comes-highly-recommended', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '50860234251c5c575ac40561b5c82a5e', '2009-09-30'),
(107, '2009-10-13 15:50:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2009-10-13 16:09:51', 'andrew', 'Shark! Design M&amp;Co. Autumn windows', '', 'Shark! Design & Marketing are excited to announce that the autumn window ‘point of sale’ for fashion retailer M&Co is now in store nationwide. <a href="http://www.kuhnel.co.uk/pages/index.html" title="Kuhnel" target="_blank" >Kuhnel</a> (the retail print specialists) were awarded the POS contract by M&Co and appointed Shark! to create the visual merchandising for M&Co’s 290 store network. Our designs drew inspiration from the rich colours of peacock feathers, complementing the jewel-like and sumptuous tones of this seasons clothes. \r\n \r\n...and as the days get shorter and our thoughts turn to all things festive, don''t forget to look out for our sparkling additions to the M&Co Christmas windows! Another successful partnership with POS print production specialist <a href="http://www.kuhnel.co.uk/pages/index.html" title="Kuhnel." target="_blank" >Kuhnel.</a>', '	<p>Shark! Design &amp; Marketing are excited to announce that the autumn window ‘point of sale’ for fashion retailer M&amp;Co is now in store nationwide. <a href="http://www.kuhnel.co.uk/pages/index.html" title="Kuhnel" target="_blank" >Kuhnel</a> (the retail print specialists) were awarded the <span class="caps">POS</span> contract by M&amp;Co and appointed Shark! to create the visual merchandising for M&amp;Co’s 290 store network. Our designs drew inspiration from the rich colours of peacock feathers, complementing the jewel-like and sumptuous tones of this seasons clothes. </p>\n\n	<p>&#8230;and as the days get shorter and our thoughts turn to all things festive, don&#8217;t forget to look out for our sparkling additions to the M&amp;Co Christmas windows! Another successful partnership with <span class="caps">POS</span> print production specialist <a href="http://www.kuhnel.co.uk/pages/index.html" title="Kuhnel." target="_blank" >Kuhnel.</a></p>', 'We''re excited to announce that the autumn window campaign for fashion retailer M&Co is now in store nationwide.', '	<p>We&#8217;re excited to announce that the autumn window campaign for fashion retailer M&amp;Co is now in store nationwide.</p>', '143', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-design-mco-autumn-windows', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '9f823ef48571cfb9042710005b2507fb', '2009-10-13'),
(108, '2009-10-28 17:23:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2013-08-09 09:58:34', 'andrew', 'Shark! grow mo''s for dough', '', 'Never shy of a challenge (especially for a good cause) the boys at Shark Design are relinquishing their razors and banishing their barbers for 30 days to grow moustaches. For the whole of Movember (once known as November), the guys will be sporting such luminary ‘lady ticklers’ as The Magnum, The Mansell and the ever refined Errol Flynn in aid of raising awareness and funds for men’s health – specifically prostate cancer.\r\n\r\nPlease show us some support by donating to our team <a href="http://uk.movember.com/mospace/157007" title="The Main Machine" target="_blank" >The Main Machine</a> and we will be posting up pictures of their weekly progress! \r\n \r\nIf you would like to learn more about Movember go to <a href=" http://uk.movember.com" title=" http://uk.movember.com" target="_blank" > http://uk.movember.com</a>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '	<p>Never shy of a challenge (especially for a good cause) the boys at Shark Design are relinquishing their razors and banishing their barbers for 30 days to grow moustaches. For the whole of Movember (once known as November), the guys will be sporting such luminary ‘lady ticklers’ as The Magnum, The Mansell and the ever refined Errol Flynn in aid of raising awareness and funds for men’s health – specifically prostate cancer.</p>\n\n	<p>Please show us some support by donating to our team <a href="http://uk.movember.com/mospace/157007" title="The Main Machine" target="_blank" >The Main Machine</a> and we will be posting up pictures of their weekly progress! </p>\n\n	<p>If you would like to learn more about Movember go to <a href=" http://uk.movember.com" title=" http://uk.movember.com" target="_blank" > http://uk.movember.com</a></p>', 'Never shy of a challenge (especially for a good cause) the boys at Shark Design are relinquishing their razors for 30 days to grow moustaches.', '	<p>Never shy of a challenge (especially for a good cause) the boys at Shark Design are relinquishing their razors for 30 days to grow moustaches.</p>', '174', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-grow-mos-for-dough', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'bb56cb5cffa49a8ca5bd5d05fef7c9a1', '2009-10-28'),
(109, '2009-11-11 13:39:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Andrew', '2013-08-09 09:58:23', 'andrew', 'Moustache Update', '', 'Well it''s been a week of controversy at Moustache mansions, Andy Mac shaved his tash off, probably because he looked more like Higgins than Magnum P.I. and Ogden shaved his cooky duster off after comparisons with Rafa Benitez and a possible breaking of the rules with an illegal Goatie! \r\n\r\nThe rest of the team are still going strong though, hats off to Mark who’s still sporting his Ginger lip warmer and a round of applause to Rolfey who’s brought in the biggest amount of sponsorship so far (although no one here seen the tash as yet – What is he hiding – Photo please). So far we’ve raised £220 towards highlighting men’s health issues, specifically prostate cancer and depression in men. \r\n\r\nAnyway, all you tashless wonders splash some cash for the tash, it’s for a good cause and you don’t have to look like a member of The Village People like we do!!\r\n\r\n"You can check our progress and images here":http://uk.movember.com/mospace/members/search/q/the+main+machine\r\n\r\n"If you want to donate to the team go here":https://www.movember.com/uk/donate/your-details/team_id/31601', '	<p>Well it&#8217;s been a week of controversy at Moustache mansions, Andy Mac shaved his tash off, probably because he looked more like Higgins than Magnum P.I. and Ogden shaved his cooky duster off after comparisons with Rafa Benitez and a possible breaking of the rules with an illegal Goatie! </p>\n\n	<p>The rest of the team are still going strong though, hats off to Mark who’s still sporting his Ginger lip warmer and a round of applause to Rolfey who’s brought in the biggest amount of sponsorship so far (although no one here seen the tash as yet – What is he hiding – Photo please). So far we’ve raised £220 towards highlighting men’s health issues, specifically prostate cancer and depression in men. </p>\n\n	<p>Anyway, all you tashless wonders splash some cash for the tash, it’s for a good cause and you don’t have to look like a member of The Village People like we do!!</p>\n\n	<p><a href="http://uk.movember.com/mospace/members/search/q/the+main+machine">You can check our progress and images here</a></p>\n\n	<p><a href="https://www.movember.com/uk/donate/your-details/team_id/31601">If you want to donate to the team go here</a></p>', 'Well it''s been a week of controversy at Moustache mansions...', '	<p>Well it&#8217;s been a week of controversy at Moustache mansions&#8230;</p>', '182', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'moustache-update', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '3dce93dce1f68934eadc0f5cc6257e87', '2009-11-11'),
(112, '2009-12-21 14:03:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Andrew', '2013-08-09 09:57:25', 'andrew', 'Movember Finale', '', 'A huge thank you to everyone who joined the Moustache Massive and everyone else who donated their hard earned cash to help us highlight men’s health issues, specifically prostate cancer and depression in men! So far we’ve raised just over £747.50 just by growing a few flavour savers. The Movember initiative has raised an amazing £3,614,226 so far in the UK alone, with much more worldwide, so props all round and here’s to next years crop of cookie dusters!\r\n\r\nWell done to John Rolfe who topped the sponsorship leaderboard with a whopping £297.50. \r\n\r\n...and finally thanks to Doug for providing us with the Movember finale image!', '	<p>A huge thank you to everyone who joined the Moustache Massive and everyone else who donated their hard earned cash to help us highlight men’s health issues, specifically prostate cancer and depression in men! So far we’ve raised just over £747.50 just by growing a few flavour savers. The Movember initiative has raised an amazing £3,614,226 so far in the UK alone, with much more worldwide, so props all round and here’s to next years crop of cookie dusters!</p>\n\n	<p>Well done to John Rolfe who topped the sponsorship leaderboard with a whopping £297.50. </p>\n\n	<p>&#8230;and finally thanks to Doug for providing us with the Movember finale image!</p>', 'A huge thank you to everyone who joined the Moustache Massive and everyone else who donated their hard earned cash ', '	<p>A huge thank you to everyone who joined the Moustache Massive and everyone else who donated their hard earned cash </p>', '190', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'movember-finale', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '3aa359758aa642874e625d9ded7077f2', '2009-12-21'),
(110, '2009-11-19 17:18:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Andrew', '2010-02-18 12:24:57', 'andrew', 'M&amp;Co. Christmas Windows', '', 'M&Co. awarded <a href="http://www.kuhnel.co.uk/pages/index.html" title="Kuhnel" target="_blank" >Kuhnel</a>  (the retail print specialists) and Shark! their prestigious Christmas window point of sale campaign following a 3-way pitch in London. \r\n\r\nThe Kuhnel–Shark! partnership were appointed after demonstrating a clear understanding of the brand and target audience and their considerable POS production expertise. \r\n\r\nThe brief - to create striking and innovative POS to ‘illuminate’ ALL windows in ALL 290 stores. \r\n\r\nOur “Christmas Morning” theme with die-cut Christmas trees, present stacks, santa’s sleigh and stockings captures the magic of the moment. By combining this with eye-catching 3D elements using metallic and fluorescent inks and sparkling LED’s we created a truly memorable experience for shoppers.\r\n \r\nDon’t just take our word for it though. M&Co. were so pleased with the Christmas campaign that they asked us to create their Autumn windows as well. Another successful Kuhnel-Shark! collaboration.  \r\n\r\nIf your in-store POS needs invigorating then why not speak to Matt on 01422 376446 or "email him":mailto:hello@sharkdesign.co.uk', '	<p>M&amp;Co. awarded <a href="http://www.kuhnel.co.uk/pages/index.html" title="Kuhnel" target="_blank" >Kuhnel</a>  (the retail print specialists) and Shark! their prestigious Christmas window point of sale campaign following a 3-way pitch in London. </p>\n\n	<p>The Kuhnel–Shark! partnership were appointed after demonstrating a clear understanding of the brand and target audience and their considerable <span class="caps">POS</span> production expertise. </p>\n\n	<p>The brief &#8211; to create striking and innovative <span class="caps">POS</span> to ‘illuminate’ <span class="caps">ALL</span> windows in <span class="caps">ALL</span> 290 stores. </p>\n\n	<p>Our “Christmas Morning” theme with die-cut Christmas trees, present stacks, santa’s sleigh and stockings captures the magic of the moment. By combining this with eye-catching 3D elements using metallic and fluorescent inks and sparkling LED’s we created a truly memorable experience for shoppers.</p>\n\n	<p>Don’t just take our word for it though. M&amp;Co. were so pleased with the Christmas campaign that they asked us to create their Autumn windows as well. Another successful Kuhnel-Shark! collaboration.  </p>\n\n	<p>If your in-store <span class="caps">POS</span> needs invigorating then why not speak to Matt on 01422 376446 or <a href="mailto:hello@sharkdesign.co.uk">email him</a></p>', 'M&Co. awarded Kuhnel and Shark! their prestigious Christmas window point of sale campaign following a 3-way pitch in London. ', '	<p>M&amp;Co. awarded Kuhnel and Shark! their prestigious Christmas window point of sale campaign following a 3-way pitch in London. </p>', '183,184,185,186,187', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'mco-christmas-windows', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '7b62dca1c3a4889006b17e891cb3ba06', '2009-11-19'),
(111, '2009-11-19 17:23:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Andrew', '2009-11-25 14:27:31', 'andrew', 'M&amp;Co. Christmas Windows', '', 'The Shark! Design and Kuhnel partnership continues with the unveiling of the Christmas window displays for fashion retailer M&Co.\r\n\r\nWith Christmas their highest profile campaign of the year, M&Co. appointed us to create innovative, striking and illuminating POS to work across their 290 strong store network.\r\n\r\n"Click here to see the full case study":http://www.sharkdesign.co.uk/case-studies/mco-christmas-windows\r\n\r\n', '	<p>The Shark! Design and Kuhnel partnership continues with the unveiling of the Christmas window displays for fashion retailer M&amp;Co.</p>\n\n	<p>With Christmas their highest profile campaign of the year, M&amp;Co. appointed us to create innovative, striking and illuminating <span class="caps">POS</span> to work across their 290 strong store network.</p>\n\n	<p><a href="http://www.sharkdesign.co.uk/case-studies/mco-christmas-windows">Click here to see the full case study</a></p>\n\n', 'The Shark! Design and Kuhnel partnership continues with the unveiling of the Christmas window displays for fashion retailer M&Co.', '	<p>The Shark! Design and Kuhnel partnership continues with the unveiling of the Christmas window displays for fashion retailer M&amp;Co.</p>', '175', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'mco-christmas-windowns', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '11319cd21f6a4938998ee7c4ea06496c', '2009-11-19'),
(113, '2009-12-21 14:03:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Andrew', '2010-02-18 12:10:16', 'andrew', 'The Terberg Magazine Is Online', '', 'Terberg asked us to design their *140 years* celebration newsletter. Their brief, to engage the reader, bring the content to life and create stand-out from the competition. \r\n\r\nOnly available online you can take a look by clicking here - <a href="http://issuu.com/sharkdesign/docs/terberg_news_issue_4?viewMode=magazine&mode=embed" title="Terberg Magazine" target="_blank" >*Terberg News Magazine*</a>\r\n\r\nAlisdair Couper (MD) and his team at Terberg DTS were delighted with their commemorative edition.\r\n\r\n', '	<p>Terberg asked us to design their <strong>140 years</strong> celebration newsletter. Their brief, to engage the reader, bring the content to life and create stand-out from the competition. </p>\n\n	<p>Only available online you can take a look by clicking here &#8211; <a href="http://issuu.com/sharkdesign/docs/terberg_news_issue_4?viewMode=magazine&mode=embed" title="Terberg Magazine" target="_blank" ><strong>Terberg News Magazine</strong></a></p>\n\n	<p>Alisdair Couper (MD) and his team at Terberg <span class="caps">DTS</span> were delighted with their commemorative edition.</p>\n\n', 'Terberg asked us to design their *140 years* celebration newsletter. Their brief, to engage the reader, bring the content to life and create stand-out from the competition. \r\n', '	<p>Terberg asked us to design their <strong>140 years</strong> celebration newsletter. Their brief, to engage the reader, bring the content to life and create stand-out from the competition. </p>', '189', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'the-terberg-magazine-is-online', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '927796c51723e4acbaf6ab1cdf67201c', '2009-12-21'),
(117, '2010-07-15 12:43:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2010-07-15 12:43:40', 'Andrew', 'The Yorkshire Saucery – website expansion!', '', 'Such has been the success of the new The Yorkshire Saucery brand (created by us!) that Shark Design have had to extend the website (designed and built by us!) to showcase the new sauces in the range. Take a look <a href="http://www.theyorkshiresaucery.co.uk" target="_blank" >here... </a>', '	<p>Such has been the success of the new The Yorkshire Saucery brand (created by us!) that Shark Design have had to extend the website (designed and built by us!) to showcase the new sauces in the range. Take a look <a href="http://www.theyorkshiresaucery.co.uk" target="_blank" >here&#8230; </a></p>', 'Such has been the success of the new The Yorkshire Saucery brand (created by us!) ', '	<p>Such has been the success of the new The Yorkshire Saucery brand (created by us!) </p>', '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'the-yorkshire-saucery-website-expansion', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '2b11d78f28b52150e40e2e46f5d082fd', '2010-07-15'),
(118, '2010-07-26 17:41:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2010-07-26 17:41:12', 'andrew', 'Shark goes back to school!', '', 'Shark Design opened its doors recently to four competition winners from Queen Elizabeth Grammar School in Wakefield. The boys, aged 7-11, each designed a front cover for an imaginary magazine of their choice and then spent the day with us in studio creating the centre spread for their new school magazine where their fantastic winning entries will appear. Watch this space to see the new magazine – coming soon!', '	<p>Shark Design opened its doors recently to four competition winners from Queen Elizabeth Grammar School in Wakefield. The boys, aged 7-11, each designed a front cover for an imaginary magazine of their choice and then spent the day with us in studio creating the centre spread for their new school magazine where their fantastic winning entries will appear. Watch this space to see the new magazine – coming soon!</p>', 'Shark Design opened its doors recently to four competition winners from Queen Elizabeth Grammar School in Wakefield.', '	<p>Shark Design opened its doors recently to four competition winners from Queen Elizabeth Grammar School in Wakefield.</p>', '41', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-goes-back-to-school', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '96ebc5dad169527b0ae8750e312a5f5d', '2010-07-15'),
(119, '2010-11-21 15:27:32', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2011-08-31 17:36:36', 'andrew', 'PPG Retail Europe (Spring/Summer)', '', 'Shark Design & Marketing were appointed by a global paint manufacturer to create new marketing literature. The brief: to design and print an eye-catching and environmentally responsible pack to showcase new colours and hold supporting literature. Our understated but impressive packaging and booklet are both printed on recycled materials with colour fan decks providing an easy to use colour guide.\r\n\r\nAnd here’s what the client thought……\r\n\r\nThe team at Shark demonstrated such passion and commitment every step of the way. From the initial concepts and ideas stage, to the design and development process and through to production. Their knowledge, creativity and ‘can do’ attitude alongside excellent project management skills, were the perfect balance to provide the level of support required to deliver this challenging brief. The stylish end result was completed to the highest standard and was admired by colleagues and clients alike. \r\n\r\nClare Howard, Colour Forecast Manager.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n', '	<p>Shark Design &amp; Marketing were appointed by a global paint manufacturer to create new marketing literature. The brief: to design and print an eye-catching and environmentally responsible pack to showcase new colours and hold supporting literature. Our understated but impressive packaging and booklet are both printed on recycled materials with colour fan decks providing an easy to use colour guide.</p>\n\n	<p>And here’s what the client thought……</p>\n\n	<p>The team at Shark demonstrated such passion and commitment every step of the way. From the initial concepts and ideas stage, to the design and development process and through to production. Their knowledge, creativity and ‘can do’ attitude alongside excellent project management skills, were the perfect balance to provide the level of support required to deliver this challenging brief. The stylish end result was completed to the highest standard and was admired by colleagues and clients alike. </p>\n\n	<p>Clare Howard, Colour Forecast Manager.</p>\n\n', 'Shark Design & Marketing were chosen by a global paint manufacturer to design new marketing literature.', '	<p>Shark Design &amp; Marketing were chosen by a global paint manufacturer to design new marketing literature.</p>', '233,231,208,204,207', 'Design-For-Print', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'shark-design-colour-trend-literature', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '80d0fd83e7d17bef308359065bb75b66', '2011-01-18'),
(120, '2011-01-19 10:21:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2011-08-02 14:12:48', 'andrew', 'Retail Display Unit', '', 'Tasked with designing and printing a free standing display unit (FSDU) to promote a new range of paints, Shark Design created this eye-catching semi-permanent unit to hold tester pots and product information brochures.\r\n \r\nThroughout this design and print project, from initial concepts to printed prototypes, our focus was on creating a unit that would allow the client to merchandise their products in an appealing and cost effective way. Inspirational imagery was used to grab the shopper’s attention and a transparent pocket allowed the retailer to change the promotional message and pricing quickly and easily.\r\n \r\nPrinted digitally, the FSDU’s were delivered pre-merchandised to over 170 stores nationwide.\r\n\r\nIf you want to increase sales with the right in-store solutions why not give us a call? ', '	<p>Tasked with designing and printing a free standing display unit (<span class="caps">FSDU</span>) to promote a new range of paints, Shark Design created this eye-catching semi-permanent unit to hold tester pots and product information brochures.</p>\n\n	<p>Throughout this design and print project, from initial concepts to printed prototypes, our focus was on creating a unit that would allow the client to merchandise their products in an appealing and cost effective way. Inspirational imagery was used to grab the shopper’s attention and a transparent pocket allowed the retailer to change the promotional message and pricing quickly and easily.</p>\n\n	<p>Printed digitally, the FSDU’s were delivered pre-merchandised to over 170 stores nationwide.</p>\n\n	<p>If you want to increase sales with the right in-store solutions why not give us a call? </p>', 'Shark Design & Marketing were tasked with designing a free standing display unit to promote a new range of paints.', '	<p>Shark Design &amp; Marketing were tasked with designing a free standing display unit to promote a new range of paints.</p>', '220,221,222,223,224', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'ppg-retail-europe', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'e5605afea2e84dd9ef6a6e091761dac3', '2011-01-18'),
(124, '2011-08-16 11:41:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2011-09-09 10:40:59', 'andrew', 'MNB Project Solutions', '', 'MNB Project Solutions, a specialist construction and property consultancy selected Shark Design & Marketing to create a new brand identity and improve their online presence. Shark provided both the website design and website development.\r\n\r\n*Launch the site here - <a href="http://www.mnbprojects.co.uk" title="MNB Project Solutions Website" target="_blank" >MNB Project Solutions</a>*\r\n\r\n', '	<p><span class="caps">MNB</span> Project Solutions, a specialist construction and property consultancy selected Shark Design &amp; Marketing to create a new brand identity and improve their online presence. Shark provided both the website design and website development.</p>\n\n	<p><strong>Launch the site here &#8211; <a href="http://www.mnbprojects.co.uk" title="MNB Project Solutions Website" target="_blank" ><span class="caps">MNB</span> Project Solutions</a></strong></p>\n\n', 'New website goes live!', '	<p>New website goes live!</p>', '', 'Websites', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'mnb-project-solutions', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '306bf8b4b3bca9311cff595d0c8c3d50', '2011-08-16'),
(122, '2011-04-03 11:32:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2011-09-09 16:39:36', 'andrew', 'PPG Retail Europe (Autumn/Winter)', '', 'Global paint manufacturer PPG Retail Europe appointed Shark to design and print their interior colour trends literature for Autumn/Winter 2011. To reflect these times of austerity our design was understated and discreet with the trends captured across five postcards, housed within an envelope. With on-going consideration to sustainability the postcards were printed on recycled paper, with the envelope made from a unique rubber textured material with subtle foil blocking.\r\n\r\nFor internal personnel, Shark designed a more detailed document using evocative imagery and insights to tell the trend theme stories. Created in a digital format this was uploaded to PPG''s intranet for use across Europe. ', '	<p>Global paint manufacturer <span class="caps">PPG</span> Retail Europe appointed Shark to design and print their interior colour trends literature for Autumn/Winter 2011. To reflect these times of austerity our design was understated and discreet with the trends captured across five postcards, housed within an envelope. With on-going consideration to sustainability the postcards were printed on recycled paper, with the envelope made from a unique rubber textured material with subtle foil blocking.</p>\n\n	<p>For internal personnel, Shark designed a more detailed document using evocative imagery and insights to tell the trend theme stories. Created in a digital format this was uploaded to <span class="caps">PPG</span>&#8217;s intranet for use across Europe. </p>', 'Global paint manufacturer PPG Retail Europe appointed Shark to design INSERT INTO `textpattern` (`ID`, `Posted`, `Expires`, `AuthorID`, `LastMod`, `LastModID`, `Title`, `Title_html`, `Body`, `Body_html`, `Excerpt`, `Excerpt_html`, `Image`, `Category1`, `Category2`, `Annotate`, `AnnotateInvite`, `comments_count`, `Status`, `textile_body`, `textile_excerpt`, `Section`, `override_form`, `Keywords`, `url_title`, `custom_1`, `custom_2`, `custom_3`, `custom_4`, `custom_5`, `custom_6`, `custom_7`, `custom_8`, `custom_9`, `custom_10`, `uid`, `feed_time`) VALUES
(135, '2012-06-14 11:54:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'kevin', '2012-06-14 12:42:00', 'kevin', 'Cookies', '', '1. How to control and delete cookies:\r\n\r\nWe will not use cookies to collect personally identifiable information about you. However, if you wish to restrict or block cookies which are set by Shark, or indeed any other website, you can do this through your browser settings, for further information please visit http://www.aboutcookies.org/.\r\n\r\n2. What we use cookies for:\r\n\r\nShark! uses Google Analytics, a web analytics service provided by Google, to evaluate your use of our site anonymously. This service sets cookies so this information can be evaluated.\r\n', '	<p>1. How to control and delete cookies:</p>\n\n	<p>We will not use cookies to collect personally identifiable information about you. However, if you wish to restrict or block cookies which are set by Shark, or indeed any other website, you can do this through your browser settings, for further information please visit http://www.aboutcookies.org/.</p>\n\n	<p>2. What we use cookies for:</p>\n\n	<p>Shark! uses Google Analytics, a web analytics service provided by Google, to evaluate your use of our site anonymously. This service sets cookies so this information can be evaluated.</p>', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'get-info', '', '', 'cookies', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '7b3c3d278849b4252dbe04c7086bf687', '2012-06-14'),
(137, '2012-07-25 12:26:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2012-08-03 16:54:35', 'andrew', 'Queen Elizabeth Grammar School', '', 'Following the success of their new look school magazine, QEGS Junior School also asked Shark to design and print their prestigious Centenary Edition.\r\n\r\nAs part of their 100 year celebrations, we designed a memorable publication showcasing everything that happened in the school over the last year. Printed on an uncoated stock for understated elegance the 100 pages (see what we did there!) were perfect bound to create a keepsake for teachers, pupils and parents.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n', '	<p>Following the success of their new look school magazine, <span class="caps">QEGS</span> Junior School also asked Shark to design and print their prestigious Centenary Edition.</p>\n\n	<p>As part of their 100 year celebrations, we designed a memorable publication showcasing everything that happened in the school over the last year. Printed on an uncoated stock for understated elegance the 100 pages (see what we did there!) were perfect bound to create a keepsake for teachers, pupils and parents.</p>', 'Following the success of their new look school magazine, QEGS Junior School also asked Shark to design and print their prestigious Centenary Edition.\r\n\r\n', '	<p>Following the success of their new look school magazine, <span class="caps">QEGS</span> Junior School also asked Shark to design and print their prestigious Centenary Edition.</p>', '310,', 'Design-For-Print', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'queen-elizabeth-grammar-school', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '60310942aa3dacddda30c59db0e0dffd', '2012-07-25'),
(143, '2012-12-05 10:43:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2012-12-05 10:50:28', 'andrew', 'Retail Direct Marketing Campaign', '', 'Luxury brands demand the highest levels of design and print quality in their customer communications.\r\n\r\nAppointed by a Jewellery and Timepiece specialist to design the invitation and envelope for their prestigious Rolex event we created this discreet mailing using a stunning embossed paper with gold foil block for true exclusivity. Hand written envelopes provided a personal finishing touch. \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n', '	<p>Luxury brands demand the highest levels of design and print quality in their customer communications.</p>\n\n	<p>Appointed by a Jewellery and Timepiece specialist to design the invitation and envelope for their prestigious Rolex event we created this discreet mailing using a stunning embossed paper with gold foil block for true exclusivity. Hand written envelopes provided a personal finishing touch. </p>', 'Luxury brands demand the highest levels of design and print quality in their customer communications.\r\n\r\n', '	<p>Luxury brands demand the highest levels of design and print quality in their customer communications.</p>', '330', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'retail-direct-marketing-campaign', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '823903481059e137a991ae7f0a50630e', '2012-12-04'),
(139, '2012-11-27 12:09:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2012-11-27 14:46:35', 'andrew', 'Retail Point of Sale', '', 'Effective POINT OF SALE material is fundamental to promoting sales and can often be the difference between influencing a purchasing decision or not. At Shark we design stand-out retail graphics that grab shopper attention, increase awareness and guide customers in-store.\r\n\r\nWe were recently appointed by a brand owner to help give their products improved aisle presence. In designing new look packaging and point of sale (hanging boards, floor vinyls, shelf talkers and aisle fins) material we gave their product range a complete makeover and increased stopping power – take a look for yourself at the images above.\r\n\r\nIf you need help designing and developing a successful visual marketing campaign why not give us a call?\r\n', '	<p>Effective <span class="caps">POINT</span> OF <span class="caps">SALE</span> material is fundamental to promoting sales and can often be the difference between influencing a purchasing decision or not. At Shark we design stand-out retail graphics that grab shopper attention, increase awareness and guide customers in-store.</p>\n\n	<p>We were recently appointed by a brand owner to help give their products improved aisle presence. In designing new look packaging and point of sale (hanging boards, floor vinyls, shelf talkers and aisle fins) material we gave their product range a complete makeover and increased stopping power – take a look for yourself at the images above.</p>\n\n	<p>If you need help designing and developing a successful visual marketing campaign why not give us a call?</p>', 'Effective POINT OF SALE material is fundamental to promoting sales and can often be the difference between influencing a purchasing decision or not. At Shark we design stand-out retail graphics that grab shopper attention, increase awareness and guide customers in-store.\r\n\r\n', '	<p>Effective <span class="caps">POINT</span> OF <span class="caps">SALE</span> material is fundamental to promoting sales and can often be the difference between influencing a purchasing decision or not. At Shark we design stand-out retail graphics that grab shopper attention, increase awareness and guide customers in-store.</p>', '325,318,319,320,322', 'Design-For-Print', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'new-ivory', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '9deb5b415a1156d0ac3390aad006398e', '2012-11-16'),
(140, '2012-11-16 10:12:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2012-11-16 10:13:12', 'andrew', 'Lister Horsfall', '', 'Luxury brands demand the highest levels of design and print quality in their customer communications.\r\n \r\nAppointed by a Jewellery and Timepiece specialist to design the invitation and envelope for their prestigious Rolex event we created this discreet mailing using a stunning embossed paper with gold foil block for true exclusivity. Hand written envelopes provided a personal finishing touch. \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n', '	<p>Luxury brands demand the highest levels of design and print quality in their customer communications.</p>\n\n	<p>Appointed by a Jewellery and Timepiece specialist to design the invitation and envelope for their prestigious Rolex event we created this discreet mailing using a stunning embossed paper with gold foil block for true exclusivity. Hand written envelopes provided a personal finishing touch. </p>', 'Luxury brands demand the highest levels of design and print quality in their customer communications.\r\n', '	<p>Luxury brands demand the highest levels of design and print quality in their customer communications.</p>', '', 'Design-For-Print', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'lister-horsfall', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '31083b942c66af88c1c7aea500b6261e', '2012-11-16'),
(141, '2012-11-21 16:03:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2012-11-27 14:47:18', 'andrew', 'Viva Las Vegas!', '', 'With a little bit of thought, design flair and production wizardry even the smallest exhibition spaces can be transformed!\r\n\r\nWorking within a 10ft square footprint we created this stand for the world’s largest mining exhibition in Las Vegas.\r\n\r\nHigh impact graphics, sweeping fascia and suspended ceiling with spotlights gave our client a stand they were proud of and visitors couldn’t ignore. We even manufactured lightweight replicas of our client’s product (real drill hammers weigh up to a tonne) to display in the corner alcove.\r\n\r\nP.S. We also arranged for local contractors to assemble and dismantle the stand, fit carpet, install electrics and even provide refreshments so our client had nothing to worry about other than enjoying the bright lights of Vegas!\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n', '	<p>With a little bit of thought, design flair and production wizardry even the smallest exhibition spaces can be transformed!</p>\n\n	<p>Working within a 10ft square footprint we created this stand for the world’s largest mining exhibition in Las Vegas.</p>\n\n	<p>High impact graphics, sweeping fascia and suspended ceiling with spotlights gave our client a stand they were proud of and visitors couldn’t ignore. We even manufactured lightweight replicas of our client’s product (real drill hammers weigh up to a tonne) to display in the corner alcove.</p>\n\n	<p>P.S. We also arranged for local contractors to assemble and dismantle the stand, fit carpet, install electrics and even provide refreshments so our client had nothing to worry about other than enjoying the bright lights of Vegas!</p>', 'With a little bit of thought, design flair and production wizardry even the smallest exhibition spaces can be transformed!', '	<p>With a little bit of thought, design flair and production wizardry even the smallest exhibition spaces can be transformed!</p>', '313,314,315,316,317', 'Design-For-Print', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'viva-las-vegas', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '2c87dd244dd1b8643b2cc56d01f23903', '2012-11-16'),
(142, '2012-11-27 12:19:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2014-02-21 10:32:59', 'andrew', 'Exhibitions', '', 'Industry statistics show that exhibition visitors decide within just a few seconds whether or not to go onto your stand. High impact, quality exhibition graphics not only transform your stand but directly reflect your brand.\r\n\r\nFrom the initial stand design through to printing, delivery and build we ensure you have everything you need to exhibit professionally and communicate effectively.\r\n\r\nHaving recently designed stands for shows in Las Vegas and Dubai distance is no object either!!\r\n\r\nIf you''re looking to create stand out at an exhibition or trade show, why not let us show you what we can do!\r\n\r\n', '	<p>Industry statistics show that exhibition visitors decide within just a few seconds whether or not to go onto your stand. High impact, quality exhibition graphics not only transform your stand but directly reflect your brand.</p>\n\n	<p>From the initial stand design through to printing, delivery and build we ensure you have everything you need to exhibit professionally and communicate effectively.</p>\n\n	<p>Having recently designed stands for shows in Las Vegas and Dubai distance is no object either!!</p>\n\n	<p>If you&#8217;re looking to create stand out at an exhibition or trade show, why not let us show you what we can do!</p>', '', '', '411,409,405,357,342,326,327,328,345,329', 'exhibitions', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'portfolio', '', '', 'exhibitions', '05', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'c5b02e328881bf46b0d3a4f5584e62fe', '2012-11-27'),
(144, '2012-12-06 09:31:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2012-12-06 09:31:45', 'andrew', 'Christmas ‘Comes Early’ Event', '', '', '', '', '', '334,333,335,332,331', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'christmas-comes-early-event', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0499fe16d5340c18ccfa3be922750fc3', '2012-12-06'),
(145, '2013-02-07 13:57:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2013-02-07 14:49:51', 'andrew', 'PING TV Wall', '', 'Shark designed this bespoke stand for PING to promote their latest range of golf clubs and custom fit service.\r\n\r\nOur versatile unit combines integral TV screen for promotional video, with custom made fittings for merchandising product and interchangeable high impact graphics to create an effective way of emphasising the clients brand and message.   \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n', '	<p>Shark designed this bespoke stand for <span class="caps">PING</span> to promote their latest range of golf clubs and custom fit service.</p>\n\n	<p>Our versatile unit combines integral TV screen for promotional video, with custom made fittings for merchandising product and interchangeable high impact graphics to create an effective way of emphasising the clients brand and message.   </p>', 'Looking for an eye-catching way to display products in-store or create a buzz at a press launch, trade show or exhibition?\r\n', '	<p>Looking for an eye-catching way to display products in-store or create a buzz at a press launch, trade show or exhibition?</p>', '342', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'ping-tv-wall', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'e3cc7067e199b0c226c480710dfa30bd', '2013-02-07'),
(146, '2013-05-01 11:14:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2013-05-01 17:17:51', 'andrew', 'RRAM Energy', '', 'RRAM Energy are a renewable energy production and investment business with solar farms nationwide. \r\n\r\nShark were asked to create a new corporate identity with an institutional feel that also reflected their roots in solar power. Our design features a strong typeface complimented by attention grabbing flashes simulating the suns rays. These flashes are also act as a flexible device for spotlighting information - in this instance the contact details on their business cards. Their new website is coming soon so be sure to come back for a look!   \r\n \r\n', '	<p><span class="caps">RRAM</span> Energy are a renewable energy production and investment business with solar farms nationwide. </p>\n\n	<p>Shark were asked to create a new corporate identity with an institutional feel that also reflected their roots in solar power. Our design features a strong typeface complimented by attention grabbing flashes simulating the suns rays. These flashes are also act as a flexible device for spotlighting information &#8211; in this instance the contact details on their business cards. Their new website is coming soon so be sure to come back for a look!   </p>', 'We recently created a new corporate identity for a national renewable energy business. Take a look!\r\n\r\n', '	<p>We recently created a new corporate identity for a national renewable energy business. Take a look!</p>', '346', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'rram-energy', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '2bb5240fff5074dde74066576e7efd42', '2013-05-01'),
(147, '2013-07-11 11:00:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2013-07-11 15:53:31', 'andrew', 'On trend again!', '', 'Shark Design were appointed by a national retailer to help their buying teams ‘look in to the future’ by designing an inspirational trend guide offering product, colour and material direction for the following 12 months. Our design used a blend of evocative imagery, colour palettes and material swatches to provide insight in to forthcoming trends and themes. One hundred pages of information were housed in a stunning binder (420mm square in size!) to create a memorable and instantly recognizable resource for the business.  \r\n\r\n', '	<p>Shark Design were appointed by a national retailer to help their buying teams ‘look in to the future’ by designing an inspirational trend guide offering product, colour and material direction for the following 12 months. Our design used a blend of evocative imagery, colour palettes and material swatches to provide insight in to forthcoming trends and themes. One hundred pages of information were housed in a stunning binder (420mm square in size!) to create a memorable and instantly recognizable resource for the business.  </p>', 'Shark Design were appointed by national retailer ''Wilkinson'' to design an inspirational trend guide!', '	<p>Shark Design were appointed by national retailer &#8216;Wilkinson&#8217; to design an inspirational trend guide!</p>', '351,352,353,355,354', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'shark-design-is-on-trend-again', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '41dba8fb7b7fbf0a361bcf0695091375', '2013-07-11'),
(148, '2013-07-11 15:26:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2013-07-11 15:55:17', 'andrew', 'Marketing Week Live', '', 'We were recently asked to design an "exhibition stand":portfolio/exhibitions and "corporate literature":portfolio/design-for-print for a client exhibiting at the Marketing Week Live event at Olympia in London. Their brief challenged us to create a stand that would not only be memorable and showcase their capabilities in a quirky way but also reflect their Yorkshire roots.\r\n \r\nAs their stand was located in the retail zone and many retailers and retail brands were attending, our idea centered on creating our very own ''retail'' outlet in the form of a traditional corner shop. \r\n \r\nTaking some of our inspiration from the ''Open All Hours'' TV series (itself inspired by a shop in Doncaster) we re-created everyone''s favourite corner shop exterior. Replacing the main shop window with a six screen TV wall (to run a video show reel) and building a separate bay window to display actual products the setting was completed with brick effect wallpaper, a cobbled street effect floor vinyl plus replica street light, letterbox, newspaper stand and A-board all engineered from cardboard.\r\n \r\nHave a look at the pictures above and if you''d like us to help you bring your exhibition space to life don''t hesitate to give us a call on 01422 376446.', '	<p>We were recently asked to design an <a href="http://www.sharkdesign.co.uk/portfolio/exhibitions">exhibition stand</a> and <a href="http://www.sharkdesign.co.uk/portfolio/design-for-print">corporate literature</a> for a client exhibiting at the Marketing Week Live event at Olympia in London. Their brief challenged us to create a stand that would not only be memorable and showcase their capabilities in a quirky way but also reflect their Yorkshire roots.</p>\n\n	<p>As their stand was located in the retail zone and many retailers and retail brands were attending, our idea centered on creating our very own &#8216;retail&#8217; outlet in the form of a traditional corner shop. </p>\n\n	<p>Taking some of our inspiration from the &#8216;Open All Hours&#8217; TV series (itself inspired by a shop in Doncaster) we re-created everyone&#8217;s favourite corner shop exterior. Replacing the main shop window with a six screen TV wall (to run a video show reel) and building a separate bay window to display actual products the setting was completed with brick effect wallpaper, a cobbled street effect floor vinyl plus replica street light, letterbox, newspaper stand and A-board all engineered from cardboard.</p>\n\n	<p>Have a look at the pictures above and if you&#8217;d like us to help you bring your exhibition space to life don&#8217;t hesitate to give us a call on 01422 376446.</p>', 'We were recently asked to design an exhibition stand and corporate literature for a client exhibiting at the Marketing Week Live event at Olympia in London.', '	<p>We were recently asked to design an exhibition stand and corporate literature for a client exhibiting at the Marketing Week Live event at Olympia in London.</p>', '358,359,360,361,362', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'marketing-week-live', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0841a7104e252f18e2df7f933a5833bc', '2013-07-11'),
(149, '2013-07-11 11:48:32', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2013-07-11 11:48:32', 'andrew', 'Halco Wallpaper', '', '', '', '', '', '364,366,367,368,365', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'halco-wallpaper', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '11ce612724bb77ff2b9dd25511627f3a', '2013-07-11'),
(151, '2013-09-11 16:56:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2013-09-11 16:56:13', 'andrew', 'Hobbycraft - Back to School', '', 'National retailer Hobbycraft has a great selection of fun products for getting kids kitted out for ''Back to School.'' \r\nShark Design & Marketing were chosen to design eye-catching in-store point of sale including headers, shelf strips, posters and window kits to help drive sales across this range.\r\n\r\nUsing a combination of vibrant colours, sponge lettering (everyone remembers sponge letters!) and stationery items we gave their ''Back to School'' aisle real stand out. \r\n\r\nIf you looking to give your product ''stand out'' in a busy retail environment why not give us a call.....\r\n', '	<p>National retailer Hobbycraft has a great selection of fun products for getting kids kitted out for &#8216;Back to School.&#8217; <br />\nShark Design &amp; Marketing were chosen to design eye-catching in-store point of sale including headers, shelf strips, posters and window kits to help drive sales across this range.</p>\n\n	<p>Using a combination of vibrant colours, sponge lettering (everyone remembers sponge letters!) and stationery items we gave their &#8216;Back to School&#8217; aisle real stand out. </p>\n\n	<p>If you looking to give your product &#8216;stand out&#8217; in a busy retail environment why not give us a call&#8230;..</p>', 'National retailer Hobbycraft has a great selection of fun products for getting kids kitted out for ''Back to School.'' \r\nShark Design & Marketing were chosen to design eye-catching in-store point of sale including headers, shelf strips, posters and window kits to help drive sales across this range.\r\n', '	<p>National retailer Hobbycraft has a great selection of fun products for getting kids kitted out for &#8216;Back to School.&#8217; <br />\nShark Design &amp; Marketing were chosen to design eye-catching in-store point of sale including headers, shelf strips, posters and window kits to help drive sales across this range.</p>', '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'hobbycraft-back-to-school', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '95a38c53fbeb5daa14837ec71f48e3bf', '2013-09-11'),
(152, '2013-09-11 17:03:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2014-02-20 17:09:08', 'andrew', 'Hobbycraft - Back to School', '', 'National retailer Hobbycraft has a great selection of fun products for getting kids kitted out for ''Back to School.''\r\n \r\nShark Design & Marketing were chosen to design eye-catching in-store point of sale including headers, shelf strips, posters and window kits to help drive sales across this new category.\r\n\r\nUsing a combination of vibrant colours, sponge lettering (everyone remembers sponge letters!) and stationery items we gave their ''Back to School'' aisle and window display a fun feel and real stand out. \r\n\r\nCreating 3D digital aisles then enabled the client to visualise how each component would look in situ before being physically printed.\r\n\r\nIf you''re looking to give your product improved presence in a busy retail environment why not give us a call.....\r\n', '	<p>National retailer Hobbycraft has a great selection of fun products for getting kids kitted out for &#8216;Back to School.&#8217;</p>\n\n	<p>Shark Design &amp; Marketing were chosen to design eye-catching in-store point of sale including headers, shelf strips, posters and window kits to help drive sales across this new category.</p>\n\n	<p>Using a combination of vibrant colours, sponge lettering (everyone remembers sponge letters!) and stationery items we gave their &#8216;Back to School&#8217; aisle and window display a fun feel and real stand out. </p>\n\n	<p>Creating 3D digital aisles then enabled the client to visualise how each component would look in situ before being physically printed.</p>\n\n	<p>If you&#8217;re looking to give your product improved presence in a busy retail environment why not give us a call&#8230;..</p>', 'National retailer Hobbycraft has a great selection of fun products for getting kids kitted out for ''Back to School.'' Shark Design & Marketing were chosen to design eye-catching in-store point of sale including headers, shelf strips, posters and window kits to help drive sales across this range.\r\n\r\n', '	<p>National retailer Hobbycraft has a great selection of fun products for getting kids kitted out for &#8216;Back to School.&#8217; Shark Design &amp; Marketing were chosen to design eye-catching in-store point of sale including headers, shelf strips, posters and window kits to help drive sales across this range.</p>', '379,380,381,382,383', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'hobbycraft-back-to-school', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'daa69c8434753cdbc438bff62d5c2106', '2013-09-11'),
(153, '2013-10-09 11:56:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2013-10-18 16:55:47', 'andrew', 'Halloweeeeeen', '', 'Halloween came early at Shark Design this year.\r\n \r\nWe had lots of fun designing spooky point of sale for one of our retail clients. From haunted castle archways, to display units containing Skeletons with flashing eyes and ghost-like aisle fins we really got in to the spirit of October 31st (albeit in August!).\r\n \r\nIf you dare, take a look at some of our scary designs above.   \r\n \r\nDon''t hesitate to give us a call if you''re looking to create a more engaging shopper experience or give your product greater impact in-store.\r\n \r\n', '	<p>Halloween came early at Shark Design this year.</p>\n\n	<p>We had lots of fun designing spooky point of sale for one of our retail clients. From haunted castle archways, to display units containing Skeletons with flashing eyes and ghost-like aisle fins we really got in to the spirit of October 31st (albeit in August!).</p>\n\n	<p>If you dare, take a look at some of our scary designs above.   </p>\n\n	<p>Don&#8217;t hesitate to give us a call if you&#8217;re looking to create a more engaging shopper experience or give your product greater impact in-store.</p>', 'Halloween came early at Shark Design this year.\r\n \r\nWe had lots of fun designing spooky point of sale for one of our retail clients. From haunted castle archways, to display units containing Skeletons with flashing eyes and ghost-like aisle fins we really got in to the spirit of October 31st (albeit in August!).\r\n', '	<p>Halloween came early at Shark Design this year.</p>\n\n	<p>We had lots of fun designing spooky point of sale for one of our retail clients. From haunted castle archways, to display units containing Skeletons with flashing eyes and ghost-like aisle fins we really got in to the spirit of October 31st (albeit in August!).</p>', '384,385,386,387,388', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'halloween', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'fce5ad820e64a214ce131037e4e39abf', '2013-10-09'),
(155, '2014-02-20 17:04:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2014-02-20 17:06:15', 'andrew', 'W&amp;L Marketing Literature', '', '', '', '', '', '390,391,392,394,395', 'Design-For-Print', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'wl-marketing-literature', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '49837cad63308cb00752f42386e1cb47', '2014-02-20'),
(156, '2014-02-21 12:01:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2014-02-21 12:01:26', 'andrew', 'Movie Production', '', 'We produced this video for the trends team at a national retailer to give their buying teams insight on forthcoming materials, colours and products. Take a look here at the final edit.', '	<p>We produced this video for the trends team at a national retailer to give their buying teams insight on forthcoming materials, colours and products. Take a look here at the final edit.</p>', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'movie-production', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'e3acb3c78216f1a87228471dc2c9909d', '2014-02-21'),
(157, '2014-03-06 14:15:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2014-03-06 14:33:31', 'andrew', 'New Marketing Literature', '', 'We designed this new brochure for one of the UK''s largest print media groups.\r\n \r\nThe brief: to showcase their work in an eye-catching way and better reflect their reputation as a creator of superb visually led experiences.\r\n\r\nTo take a look at the full brochure "click here":http://issuu.com/sharkdesign/docs/w_l_brochure?e=1444526/6058655\r\n \r\nIf you''re looking for new ways to engage prospective customers why not give us a call on 01422 376446 - I''m sure we can help deliver your message more effectively.\r\n \r\n \r\n', '	<p>We designed this new brochure for one of the UK&#8217;s largest print media groups.</p>\n\n	<p>The brief: to showcase their work in an eye-catching way and better reflect their reputation as a creator of superb visually led experiences.</p>\n\n	<p>To take a look at the full brochure <a href="http://issuu.com/sharkdesign/docs/w_l_brochure?e=1444526/6058655">click here</a></p>\n\n	<p>If you&#8217;re looking for new ways to engage prospective customers why not give us a call on 01422 376446 &#8211; I&#8217;m sure we can help deliver your message more effectively.</p>', 'We designed this new brochure for one of the UK''s largest print media groups.\r\n \r\nThe brief: to showcase their work in an eye-catching way and better reflect their reputation as a creator of superb visually led experiences.\r\n \r\n', '	<p>We designed this new brochure for one of the UK&#8217;s largest print media groups.</p>\n\n	<p>The brief: to showcase their work in an eye-catching way and better reflect their reputation as a creator of superb visually led experiences.</p>', '390,391,392,395,394', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'new-marketing-literature', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'bf62ff4b19ef48fa9eed3788093cf06f', '2014-02-21'),
(158, '2014-10-14 11:41:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2014-10-14 11:41:43', 'andrew', 'We''re HIRING! ', '', 'Looking to join the team at a fast growing creative marketing agency?\r\n\r\nAre you creative, enthusiastic and hungry to succeed? \r\n\r\nIf so then Shark! is just the place for you.\r\nWe are looking for a confident, self-starter who has a desire to learn and a passion to succeed as an **Account Executive**.\r\n\r\nSupporting the senior account management team, this opportunity will give you the chance to work with well-known brands and cover everything from brand development to direct marketing (digital/direct mail/SMS), advertising, print management and web design.\r\nYou will be responsible for the day-to-day management of key accounts, helping to deliver great campaigns, providing exceptional service to existing clients as well as engaging with new business opportunities.\r\nYou’ll be a good communicator with strong organisational and project management skills. Some experience, preferably in a creative agency environment, would be an advantage.\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n**Key Requirements**\r\n\r\n1. Digital marketing experience an advantage \r\n2. Relevant marketing qualifications to degree level\r\n3. Able to work effectively under pressure whilst maintaining attention to detai\r\n4. Ability to use own initiative and find improvements to processes\r\n5. Ability to learn and use new systems quickly\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n\r\nSalary expectations for this role are £15,000 to £19,000 dependant on experience.\r\nOther benefits of employment include 26 days annual holiday (plus statutory holidays), and after a satisfactory trial, eligibility for Pension Scheme and Profit Share. </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>To apply, please send your CV and covering letter to matthew.ogden@sharkdesign.co.uk\r\n\r\n\r\nShark! Design and Marketing is an equal opportunities employer.\r\n\r\nGood Luck!\r\n', '	<p>Looking to join the team at a fast growing creative marketing agency?</p>\n\n	<p>Are you creative, enthusiastic and hungry to succeed? </p>\n\n	<p>If so then Shark! is just the place for you.<br />\nWe are looking for a confident, self-starter who has a desire to learn and a passion to succeed as an <b>Account Executive</b>.</p>\n\n	<p>Supporting the senior account management team, this opportunity will give you the chance to work with well-known brands and cover everything from brand development to direct marketing (digital/direct mail/SMS), advertising, print management and web design.<br />\nYou will be responsible for the day-to-day management of key accounts, helping to deliver great campaigns, providing exceptional service to existing clients as well as engaging with new business opportunities.<br />\nYou’ll be a good communicator with strong organisational and project management skills. Some experience, preferably in a creative agency environment, would be an advantage.<br />\n<p></p></p>\n\n	<p><b>Key Requirements</b></p>\n\n	<p>1. Digital marketing experience an advantage <br />\n2. Relevant marketing qualifications to degree level<br />\n3. Able to work effectively under pressure whilst maintaining attention to detai<br />\n4. Ability to use own initiative and find improvements to processes<br />\n5. Ability to learn and use new systems quickly</p>\n\n	<p><p></p>\n\n	<p>Salary expectations for this role are £15,000 to £19,000 dependant on experience.<br />\nOther benefits of employment include 26 days annual holiday (plus statutory holidays), and after a satisfactory trial, eligibility for Pension Scheme and Profit Share. </p></p>\n\n	<p><b>To apply, please send your CV and covering letter to matthew.ogden@sharkdesign.co.uk</p>\n\n	<p>Shark! Design and Marketing is an equal opportunities employer.</p>\n\n	<p>Good Luck!</p>', 'Looking to join the team at a fast growing creating marketing agency?\r\n\r\nAre you creative, enthusiastic and hungry to succeed? \r\n\r\nIf so then Shark! is just the place for you.\r\nWe are looking for a confident, self-starter who has a desire to learn and a passion to succeed as an **Account Executive**.', '	<p>Looking to join the team at a fast growing creating marketing agency?</p>\n\n	<p>Are you creative, enthusiastic and hungry to succeed? </p>\n\n	<p>If so then Shark! is just the place for you.<br />\nWe are looking for a confident, self-starter who has a desire to learn and a passion to succeed as an <b>Account Executive</b>.</p>', '41', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', 'Jobs,Marketing,Advertising,Creative,CV,Agency,New Opportunity,Design,Print,Shark.', 'we-re-hiring', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '08f48459f9086ba2b17c6aa41a37f507', '2014-09-08');
