(123, '2011-04-15 13:50:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2011-08-16 11:14:45', 'andrew', 'Trinity Academy, Halifax', '', 'Trinity Academy, Halifax chose Shark to design and develop their new school website. With an emphasis on improved usability for students, staff, parents and the wider community our website design reflects the modern and engaging environment their new school building will provide on completion. Easy to use navigation combined with information presented clearly creates a positive online experience.\r\n  \r\n*Launch the site here - <a href="http://www.trinityacademyhalifax.org" title="Trinity Academy Website" target="_blank" >Trinity Academy, Halifax</a>*\r\n\r\n  ', '	<p>Trinity Academy, Halifax chose Shark to design and develop their new school website. With an emphasis on improved usability for students, staff, parents and the wider community our website design reflects the modern and engaging environment their new school building will provide on completion. Easy to use navigation combined with information presented clearly creates a positive online experience.</p>\n\n	<p><strong>Launch the site here &#8211; <a href="http://www.trinityacademyhalifax.org" title="Trinity Academy Website" target="_blank" >Trinity Academy, Halifax</a></strong></p>\n\n  ', 'Trinity Academy, Halifax appoints Shark to design and develop their new website.', '	<p>Trinity Academy, Halifax appoints Shark to design and develop their new website.</p>', '', 'Websites', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'trinity-academy-halifax', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'f8ccb2ecc438389cdf02becd7de01473', '2011-04-15'),
(127, '2011-09-13 17:12:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2013-02-07 14:06:50', 'andrew', 'PPG Digital Brochure', '', 'It doesn’t matter to us if we’re asked to design literature for print or for use digitally – we just love to design.\r\n\r\nWe created this digital brochure for a global paint manufacturer to promote next seasons'' new colours. Set the challenge of visualising how these colours could work within the home, we decided to design our very own room sets! Take a look through them in the slide show above - we''ve included some of our initial sketches so you can see where our inspiration started.\r\n \r\nOnly available online the full brochure can be seen here - <a href="http://issuu.com/sharkdesign/docs/colour_trends_2012?viewMode=magazine&mode=embed" title="Terberg Magazine" target="_blank" >*PPG digital brochure*</a>.\r\n\r\nWe were really happy with the results but more importantly, this is what the client thought:\r\n\r\n“Taking a new direction for the PPG 2012 trends project was no problem for the team at Shark! Their ability to rise to yet another challenge saw them executing a professional and creative digital brochure, which is an inspiring and exciting new way to talk about colour with colleagues and customers. I was delighted with the end result, and was proud for the recipients to receive the stylish mailer which supported the link to the brochure.”\r\n\r\nClare Howard, European Colour and Trends Forecast Manager\r\n\r\n', '	<p>It doesn’t matter to us if we’re asked to design literature for print or for use digitally – we just love to design.</p>\n\n	<p>We created this digital brochure for a global paint manufacturer to promote next seasons&#8217; new colours. Set the challenge of visualising how these colours could work within the home, we decided to design our very own room sets! Take a look through them in the slide show above &#8211; we&#8217;ve included some of our initial sketches so you can see where our inspiration started.</p>\n\n	<p>Only available online the full brochure can be seen here &#8211; <a href="http://issuu.com/sharkdesign/docs/colour_trends_2012?viewMode=magazine&mode=embed" title="Terberg Magazine" target="_blank" ><strong><span class="caps">PPG</span> digital brochure</strong></a>.</p>\n\n	<p>We were really happy with the results but more importantly, this is what the client thought:</p>\n\n	<p>“Taking a new direction for the <span class="caps">PPG</span> 2012 trends project was no problem for the team at Shark! Their ability to rise to yet another challenge saw them executing a professional and creative digital brochure, which is an inspiring and exciting new way to talk about colour with colleagues and customers. I was delighted with the end result, and was proud for the recipients to receive the stylish mailer which supported the link to the brochure.”</p>\n\n	<p>Clare Howard, European Colour and Trends Forecast Manager</p>', 'It doesn’t matter to us if we’re asked to design literature for print or for use digitally – we just love to design.\r\n', '	<p>It doesn’t matter to us if we’re asked to design literature for print or for use digitally – we just love to design.</p>', '336,337,338,339,340', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'ppg-digital-brochure', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '772b2f153826d82be3a20c350dc40a6a', '2011-09-08'),
(125, '2011-08-22 17:00:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2011-09-09 17:20:42', 'andrew', 'Global manufacturer appoints Shark', '', 'Terberg DTS UK, a global provider of specialist vehicles chose Shark to design and print their new marketing literature. The brief: engage Terberg''s audience and present their extensive product portfolio clearly and concisely. Our colour coded, stepped edge design provides a strong visual index making the readers journey to the product and information they need an easy one. \r\n\r\nThe second booklet in our newly designed suite of marketing literature is coming soon. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '	<p>Terberg <span class="caps">DTS</span> UK, a global provider of specialist vehicles chose Shark to design and print their new marketing literature. The brief: engage Terberg&#8217;s audience and present their extensive product portfolio clearly and concisely. Our colour coded, stepped edge design provides a strong visual index making the readers journey to the product and information they need an easy one. </p>\n\n	<p>The second booklet in our newly designed suite of marketing literature is coming soon. </p>\n\n', 'Terberg DTS selects Shark to design their new marketing literature', '	<p>Terberg <span class="caps">DTS</span> selects Shark to design their new marketing literature</p>', '250', 'Design-For-Print', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'terberg-dts', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'b4f04f2f2c1cc79edf38280fbe0ba897', '2011-08-22'),
(126, '2010-11-21 16:19:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2011-09-08 16:33:14', 'andrew', 'Shark design and print new colour trend literature', '', 'Shark Design & Marketing were appointed by a global paint manufacturer to design new marketing literature. The brief: to design and print an eye-catching and environmentally responsible pack to showcase new colours and hold supporting literature. Our understated but stylish packaging and booklet are both printed on recycled materials with colour fan decks providing an easy to use colour guide.\r\n\r\nAnd here’s what the client thought……\r\n\r\nThe team at Shark demonstrated such passion and commitment every step of the way. From the initial concepts and ideas stage, to the design and development process and through to production. Their knowledge, creativity and ‘can do’ attitude alongside excellent project management skills, were the perfect balance to provide the level of support required to deliver this challenging brief. The stylish end result was completed to the highest standard and was admired by colleagues and clients alike. \r\n\r\nClare Howard, Colour Forecast Manager.\r\n\r\n', '	<p>Shark Design &amp; Marketing were appointed by a global paint manufacturer to design new marketing literature. The brief: to design and print an eye-catching and environmentally responsible pack to showcase new colours and hold supporting literature. Our understated but stylish packaging and booklet are both printed on recycled materials with colour fan decks providing an easy to use colour guide.</p>\n\n	<p>And here’s what the client thought……</p>\n\n	<p>The team at Shark demonstrated such passion and commitment every step of the way. From the initial concepts and ideas stage, to the design and development process and through to production. Their knowledge, creativity and ‘can do’ attitude alongside excellent project management skills, were the perfect balance to provide the level of support required to deliver this challenging brief. The stylish end result was completed to the highest standard and was admired by colleagues and clients alike. </p>\n\n	<p>Clare Howard, Colour Forecast Manager.</p>\n\n', 'PPG Retail Europe selected Shark to design their new colour trend literature', '	<p><span class="caps">PPG</span> Retail Europe selected Shark to design their new colour trend literature</p>', '202', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'shark-designs-new-colour-trend-literature', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'c0ef887a03fc2e80e1c786e74273d50a', '2011-08-24'),
(128, '2011-09-09 13:19:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2011-09-12 11:48:36', 'andrew', 'In-Store Sales Promotion', '', 'We developed this display unit to promote a new range of paints for a DIY retailer. Eye-catching, inspirational imagery makes the unit an ‘attention grabber’ and displaying the product and information brochure together enables the shopper to make an easy and informed purchasing decision.\r\n\r\nIf you need creative ideas for any new or existing product promotional activity why not give us a call.  ', '	<p>We developed this display unit to promote a new range of paints for a <span class="caps">DIY</span> retailer. Eye-catching, inspirational imagery makes the unit an ‘attention grabber’ and displaying the product and information brochure together enables the shopper to make an easy and informed purchasing decision.</p>\n\n	<p>If you need creative ideas for any new or existing product promotional activity why not give us a call.  </p>', 'We designed and manufactured this display unit as part of a sales promotion campaign. ', '	<p>We designed and manufactured this display unit as part of a sales promotion campaign. </p>', '242', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'in-store-sales-promotion', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '0e31bd5202909c2957bdc1274dcb33c1', '2011-09-09'),
(129, '2011-12-08 14:28:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2011-12-08 14:37:38', 'andrew', 'Origin Print Solutions', '', 'Shark Design & Marketing were appointed by Origin Print Solutions – a leading regional print management company - to design a new corporate identity and website.\r\n\r\nThe brief was simple: improve their existing online presence with an easy to navigate site and password protected client area for creating and ordering personalised business stationery.\r\n\r\nThe vibrant homepage reflects Origin’s expertise managing colour, with an image rotator providing an insight to their business.\r\n\r\nTheir new corporate identity is currently being rolled out across various other pieces of literature which we will showcase on here soon!\r\n\r\n\r\nLaunch their new site here – <a href="http://www.originprintsolutions.co.uk" title="Origin Print Solutions Website" target="_blank" >Origin Print Solutions</a>\r\n\r\n', '	<p>Shark Design &amp; Marketing were appointed by Origin Print Solutions – a leading regional print management company &#8211; to design a new corporate identity and website.</p>\n\n	<p>The brief was simple: improve their existing online presence with an easy to navigate site and password protected client area for creating and ordering personalised business stationery.</p>\n\n	<p>The vibrant homepage reflects Origin’s expertise managing colour, with an image rotator providing an insight to their business.</p>\n\n	<p>Their new corporate identity is currently being rolled out across various other pieces of literature which we will showcase on here soon!</p>\n\n	<p>Launch their new site here – <a href="http://www.originprintsolutions.co.uk" title="Origin Print Solutions Website" target="_blank" >Origin Print Solutions</a></p>\n\n', 'Shark Design & Marketing were appointed by Origin Print Solutions – a leading regional print management company - to design a new corporate identity and website.\r\n', '	<p>Shark Design &amp; Marketing were appointed by Origin Print Solutions – a leading regional print management company &#8211; to design a new corporate identity and website.</p>', '251', 'Websites', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'origin-print-solutions', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '29e95ede32b5e0ed8104938f1b5c508d', '2011-12-08'),
(130, '2012-01-19 12:18:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2012-04-19 15:16:00', 'Andrew', 'SolarLex', '', 'SolarLex – designers, suppliers and installers of solar panels recently appointed Shark to design, print and build their exhibition stand and marketing literature for the Harrogate Home Building Show.\r\n\r\nTheir brief: to create an eye-catching stand and literature that reflected their brand and helped promote their products. After creating a 3D visual of the stand, we were responsible for designing and printing the wall graphics and constructing the stand. We even supplied all the furniture ready for the show!\r\n\r\nSolarLex were delighted with the results – “everything went fantastically well… very, very positive and we made loads of sales so a good weekend”.\r\n\r\nIf you’re looking for an Exhibition Stand, trade show displays, pop-up banners or other display stands why not give us a call? \r\n\r\n', '	<p>SolarLex – designers, suppliers and installers of solar panels recently appointed Shark to design, print and build their exhibition stand and marketing literature for the Harrogate Home Building Show.</p>\n\n	<p>Their brief: to create an eye-catching stand and literature that reflected their brand and helped promote their products. After creating a 3D visual of the stand, we were responsible for designing and printing the wall graphics and constructing the stand. We even supplied all the furniture ready for the show!</p>\n\n	<p>SolarLex were delighted with the results – “everything went fantastically well… very, very positive and we made loads of sales so a good weekend”.</p>\n\n	<p>If you’re looking for an Exhibition Stand, trade show displays, pop-up banners or other display stands why not give us a call? </p>\n\n', 'SolarLex – designers, suppliers and installers of solar panels recently appointed Shark to design, print and build their exhibition stand and marketing literature for the Harrogate Home Building Show.\r\n', '	<p>SolarLex – designers, suppliers and installers of solar panels recently appointed Shark to design, print and build their exhibition stand and marketing literature for the Harrogate Home Building Show.</p>', '252,253,254,255,256', 'Design-For-Print', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'solarlex-exhibition-stand-and-marketing-literature', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'fc1beb790d214568268c07373c82cd6d', '2012-01-19'),
(131, '2012-04-19 14:46:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2012-04-19 14:46:10', 'Andrew', 'Mars Chocolate (UK) Limited', '', 'Mars Chocolate (UK) invited Shark Design & Marketing to demonstrate our graphic design and print manufacturing capabilities for a range of its’ point-of-sale material – an integral part of their sales promotion activity.\r\n \r\nThe brief: to design and print free standing display units, dump bins and counter top boxes to create improved in-store presence and allow Mars to display their brands in a memorable way. Each item had to be easy to assemble, durable, meet retail guidelines and be cost effective.  \r\n\r\nOur inspirational design, eye-catching constructions, innovative print techniques and materials demonstrate how to create an exciting shopping experience through outstanding point-of-sale.\r\n', '	<p>Mars Chocolate (UK) invited Shark Design &amp; Marketing to demonstrate our graphic design and print manufacturing capabilities for a range of its’ point-of-sale material – an integral part of their sales promotion activity.</p>\n\n	<p>The brief: to design and print free standing display units, dump bins and counter top boxes to create improved in-store presence and allow Mars to display their brands in a memorable way. Each item had to be easy to assemble, durable, meet retail guidelines and be cost effective.  </p>\n\n	<p>Our inspirational design, eye-catching constructions, innovative print techniques and materials demonstrate how to create an exciting shopping experience through outstanding point-of-sale.</p>', 'Mars Chocolate (UK) invited Shark Design & Marketing to demonstrate our graphic design and print manufacturing capabilities for a range of its’ point-of-sale material – an integral part of their sales promotion activity.\r\n', '	<p>Mars Chocolate (UK) invited Shark Design &amp; Marketing to demonstrate our graphic design and print manufacturing capabilities for a range of its’ point-of-sale material – an integral part of their sales promotion activity.</p>', '282,278,279,280,281', 'Design-For-Print', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'mars-chocolate', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '5f1b45af58c6164363e3204fc6ad3da8', '2012-04-11'),
(132, '2012-05-30 10:08:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2012-07-25 11:15:44', 'andrew', 'Brilliant Literature', '', 'Brilliant - the Interiors, Living and Lighting specialist asked Shark to design and print their new marketing literature. \r\n\r\n\r\nTraditionally, the three arms of their business were promoted in a single brochure. Our design proposal focused on creating three distinct sub-brands each with their own brochure to help make Brilliants offering clearer and create greater appeal to a wider audience. As part of our design, each brochure references their complementary services to reinforce their portfolio.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n', '	<p>Brilliant &#8211; the Interiors, Living and Lighting specialist asked Shark to design and print their new marketing literature. </p>\n\n	<p>Traditionally, the three arms of their business were promoted in a single brochure. Our design proposal focused on creating three distinct sub-brands each with their own brochure to help make Brilliants offering clearer and create greater appeal to a wider audience. As part of our design, each brochure references their complementary services to reinforce their portfolio.</p>', 'Brilliant - the Interiors, Living and Lighting specialist asked Shark to design and print their new marketing literature. \r\n', '	<p>Brilliant &#8211; the Interiors, Living and Lighting specialist asked Shark to design and print their new marketing literature. </p>', '300, 302, 303, 301,304', 'Design-For-Print', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 1, 1, 'case-studies', '', '', 'brilliant', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '8521ed8d70bb3d8919c8df95e1a91f0d', '2012-05-30'),
(136, '2012-07-25 10:58:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'andrew', '2012-07-25 10:58:13', 'andrew', 'Gateways School', '', '', '', '', '', '308,', 'Design-For-Print', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'news', '', '', 'gateways-school', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'a435410ab0b2620cb1b377acb709acc9', '2012-07-25');

